hadiths[273]{hadithnumber,text}:
1819,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs maut ki tamanna na karey (kyonkey) agar wo nek hai to ho sakta hai wo aur nekiyan karey aur agar wo gunah-gaar hai to shayad wo apney Allah ko razi kar ley."
1820,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs maut ki khahish na kerey. agar wo nek hai to shayad mazeed zinda reh kar aur nekiyan karey aur ye uskey liye behtar hai. aur agar wo bura hai to shayad wo apney Allah ko razi kar ley."
1821,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs duniya mein pesh aaney wali kisi musibat aur takleef ki bina par maut ki tamanna aur dua na karey balke yun kahey : ( اللھم ! أحینی … … … خیرالی ),''aey Allah ! jab tak merey liye zindagi behtar hai, mujhey zinda rakh aur jab merey liye maut behtar ho to mujhey maut dey dey.''"
1822,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khabrdar ! tum mein sey koi shakhs pesh aaney wali takleef ki bina par maut ki khahish na kerey. agar usey laziman maut ki khahish kerni hai to yun kahe : (اللھم ! احینی … … … خیرالی),''aey Allah ! jab tak zinda rehna merey liye behtar hai, mujhey zinda rakh aur jab maut merey liye behtar ho to mujhey maut dey dey.''"
1823,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maut ki na dua karo aur na uski khahish hi karo. jis shakhs ko laziman (is qism ki) dua kerni hi ho to wo yun kahe : (اللھم ! احینی ما کانت الحیاۃ خیرالی), ''aey Allah ! jab tak merey liye zindagi behtar hai, mujhey zinda rakh aur jab wafat merey liye behtar ho to mujhey faut kar dey.''"
1824,Hazrat Qais bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaya (to dekha ke) unhoney apna pet saat jagah sey aag sey daaghaa huwa hai. unhoney farmaya : agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein maut ki dua karney sey roka na hota to main zarur maut ki dua karta.
1825,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : lazzaton ko tod deney wali (maut) ko khub yad kiya karo. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain : (sanad mein mazkur) Muhammad bin Ibrahim Abu-Bakar bin Abi Sheeba key walid hain."
1826,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jab tum maiyat key yahaan jaao to achchhi baaten karo kyonkey farishtey tumhari baaton par Aameen kehtey hain. jab (merey pehley khawind Hazrat Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey to mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main kaisey dua karun ? aap ney farmaya : to keh :(اللھم ! اغفرلنا ولہ و أعقبنی منہ Aqba حسنۃ),''aey Allah ! hamein aur isey maaf farma aur mujhey is ka achchha badal ata farma. to Allah Taala ney mujhey unkey baad Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ata farma diye.''"
1827,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maut ke qarib logon ko (La-Ilaah-illa-Allah) ki talqin karo."
1828,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maut ke qarib logon ko (La-Ilaah-illa-Allah) ki talqin karo."
1829,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin ki maut peshani key paseeney key sath hoti hai."
1830,Hazrat Barida Raziallahu anhu bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : momin maathe key paseeney key sath martaa hai.
1831,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) meri aagaush mein faut huye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat dekhney key baad main kisi key liye maut ki sakhti ko napasand nahin karti.
1832,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) (khaas khaadim) bayan kartey hain ke aakhiri nigah jo mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par dali, yun thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (darwazey ka) parda hataayaa jabkey log (subah ki namaz mein) Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key peechhey safon mein khadey they. Hazrat Abu-Bakar ney peechhey hatney ka irada kiya (ke shayad aap tashrif lana chahtey hain) to aap ney sab ko ishara kiya ke apni apni jagah namaz padhtey raho (kyonkey sab aap ki taraf dekhney lagey they) aur aap ney parda gira diya aur phir aap usi din key aakhir mein faut ho gaey. ye peer key din ki baat hai."
1833,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Madina Munawra main eik aadmi faut ho gaya jo paida bhi wahin huwa tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ka janaza padha, phir farmaya : kaash! ke ye apni paidaish wali jagah sey bahar faut hota. sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kyon? aap ney farmaya : aadmi jab apni paidaish ki jagah sey door faut hota hai to jannat mein usey uski paidaish gaah sey maut ki jagah tak ka fasla maap kar jannat di jati hai."
1834,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab momin ko maut aaney lagti hai to rehmat key farishtey safed reshmi libas ley kar uskey paas aa jatey hain aur kehtey hain : aey momin rooh ! nikal aa. to Allah Taala sey razi, Allah Taala tujh sey razi. aur chal Allah ki rehmat aur meharbani ki taraf aur pahunch aisey Rab key paas jo tujh par qatai naraz nahin hai. to wo intehai khushbudar, pakizah kastoori jaisi mehak key sath nikal aati hai yahan tak ke farishtey (khushi aur suroor sey) usey eik dusrey ko pakdaatey (hathon haath letey) hain aur isi tarah wo usey aasman key darwazey tak ley jatey hain. aasman waley farishtey kehtey hain : kis qadr khushbudar hai ye rooh jo tum zamin sey laye ho ! . phir wo usey (pehley sey faut shuda) momineen ki ruhon key paas ley aatey hain. Allah ki qism ! wo uskey aaney par is qadr khush hotey hain ke tum apney kisi ghaaieb shakhs key aaney par itney khush nahin hotey, phir wo (pehley momin) us sey poochhtey hain : falan ka kya haal hai? falan ka kya haal hai? phir wo (aapas mein) kehtey hain : chhodo usey wo to duniya key gham aur fikr mein tha. jab wo rooh kehti hai ke kya wo tumharey paas nahin aaya? (yani wo to kab ka mar chuka hai) to wo kehtey hain : ooho ! usey uskey jahannami thikaney ki janib ley jaya gaya hai. (us key muqabley mein) jab kafir ko maut aati hai to azab key farishtey gandaa badboodaar taat ley kar uskey paas aa jatey hain aur (ghussey sey) kehtey hain : nikal udhar, to bhi naraz aur tera Allah bhi tujh par naraz. chal Allah key azab ki taraf. to wo intehai badboodaar murdar laash key bhabukey key sath nikalti hai yahan tak ke wo isey zamin key darwazey par ley jatey hain aur kehtey hain : kis qadr badboodaar hai ye ! yahan tak ke wo isey (pehley sey marey huye) kafiron ki ruhon mein ley jatey hain."
1835,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi Allah Taala ki mulaqat ko pasand karta hai, Allah Taala uski mulaqat ko pasand karta hai aur jo shakhs Allah Taala ki mulaqat ko napasand karta hai, Allah Taala uski mulaqat ko napasand farmata hai. (Hazrat Abu-Hurera key shagrid ) Hazrat Shureh ney kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas hazir huwa aur arz kiya : aey Ummul-Mominin ! mainey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey eik aisi hadees bayan kartey suna hai agar wo sahih hai to hum to maarey gaey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : wo kon si hadees hai? (mainey kaha : ) wo kehtey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala ki mulaqat ko pasand karta hai, Allah Taala us sey mulaqat ko pasand farmata hai aur jo Allah Taala ki mulaqat ko napasand karta hai, Allah Taala us sey milna pasand nahin farmata. jabkey hum mein sey har eik maut ko napasand karta hai? (aur maut key baghair Allah Taala sey mulaqat mumkin nahin?) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : haqiqat mein ye alfaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaai hain, lekin is ka wo matlab nahin jo tum ney samjha hai balke ye us waqt hai jab nazar ooper uth jaey aur saans seeney mein atakney lagey aur jism key raungtey khadey ho jaeyn aur wo kaanpney lagey. (yani nazaa (jaan nikalne ke qareeb) rooh ka amal shuru ho jaey) us waqt jo shakhs Allah Taala ki mulaqat ko pasand karta hai, Allah Taala uski mulaqat ko pasand farmata hai aur jo shakhs us waqt Allah Taala ki mulaqat ko napasand karta hai, Allah Taala bhi us sey milna pasand nahin farmata."
1836,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala farmata hai : jab mera banda meri mulaqat ko pasand karta hai to main bhi us sey mulaqat ko pasand karta hun aur jab wo meri mulaqat ko napasand karta hai to main bhi us sey mulaqat ko napasand karta hun."
1837,"Hazrat Ubada (bin Saamat) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala sey milney ki khahish karta hai, Allah Taala us sey milney ki khahish karta hai aur jo shakhs Allah Taala sey milney ko napasand karta hai, Allah Taala us sey milney ko napasand karta hai."
1838,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala sey milna chahta hai, Allah Taala bhi us sey milna chahta hai aur jo shakhs Allah Taala sey milna nahin chahta Allah Taala bhi us sey milna nahin chahta."
1839,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs (nazaa (jaan nikalne ke qareeb) key waqt) Allah Taala sey milna achchha samajhta hai, Allah Taala bhi us sey milna achchha samajhta hai aur jo shakhs Allah Taala sey milna bura samajhta hai, Allah Taala bhi us sey milna bura samajhta hai. kaha gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah Taala sey milney ko napasand karney ka matlab maut ko napasand karna hai? hum mein sey to har shakhs maut ko napasand karta hai? aap ney farmaya : ye maut key waqt ki baat hai ke jab momin ko Allah Taala ki rehmat aur bakhshish ki khush-khabri di jati hai to wo fauran Allah Taala sey milna chahta hai aur Allah Taala us sey milna chahta hai aur jab kafir ko Allah key azab ki ittilaa di jati hai to wo Allah Taala sey milna napasand karta hai aur Allah Taala bhi us sey milna napasand karta hai."
1840,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat key baad aap ki aakhon key darmiyan (peshani ko) bosa diya.
1841,Hazrat ibne-Abbas aur Hazrat Aaisha Raziallahu anhu sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko bosa diya jabkey aap faut ho chukey they.
1842,"Hazrat Abu-Salma sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney mujhey khabar di ke (jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut ho gaey to) Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) (سنح) maqam par waqey apney ghar sey ghodey par aaye (taake jaldi pahunch saken) yahan tak ke wo ghodey sey utrey aur masjid mein dakhil huye aur kisi sey baat cheet nahin ki yahan tak ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaey. us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko eik dhaari daar yamni chadar sey dhanp diya gaya tha. unhoney aap key chehrey mubarak sey kapda hataayaa, phir jhuk kar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko bosa diya aur roney lagey, phir kaha : mera baap aap par qurban ! Allah ki qism ! Allah Taala aap par do dafa maut taari nahin kerega. jo maut aap key liye muqaddar thi, wo aap ko aa chuki."
1843,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jange-uahad key din merey baap ki maiyat is haal mein laee gaee ke unka chehra bigaad diya gaya tha (kafiron ney unkey chehrey key aa'zaa (ang) kaat daley they). to un ki maiyat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney rakh di gaee aur usey eik kapdey sey dhanp diya gaya. main munh sey kapda hataney ki koshish karta tha to meri qom key log mujhey roktey they. aakhir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maiyat uthaney ka hukm diya. jab maiyat uthai gaee to aap ney eik aurat key roney ki aawaz suni to farmaya : ye kon hai? logon ney kaha : ye Amr ki beti ya Amr ki behan hai. aap ney farmaya : na ro ya farmaya : kyon roti hai? maiyat key uthaey janey tak farishton ney usey apney mubarak paron sey saya kiye rakha.
1844,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki eik chhoti beti ki wafat ka waqt aaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey uthaya aur apney seeney sey lagaya, phir apna daste mubarak is par rakha. bil-aakhir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney faut ho gaeen, Hazrat Ummey Aiman (Raziallahu anha) roney lagin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Ummey Aiman ! tum roti ho jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tumharey paas hain? unhoney arz kiya : main kyon na rau'uon jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ro rahey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main (tumhari tarah) nahin ro raha balke mera ronaa to Allah Taala ki rehmat ki bina par hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin har haal mein behtar rehta hai (yahan tak ke) uski jaan nikal rahi hoti hai aur wo Allah Taala ki tareefen karta hota hai."
1845,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut huye to (aap ki lakhte-jigar) Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) roney lagin. sath sath keh rahi thin : haaey merey Abba jaan ! jo apney Rab sey kis qadr qarib they. haaye merey Abba jaan ! jin ki wafat ki ittilaa hum Hazrat Jibril alehissalam ko bhi detey hain. haaye merey Abba jaan ! jin ka thikana jannatul firdaus ban chuka.
1846,"Hazrat Jabir (bin Abdullah) Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke merey walid mohtaram (Raziallahu anhu) uhad key din shaheed huye. main unkey chehrey sey kapda hataataa tha aur rotaa tha, log mujhey roktey they jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey nahin roktey they. meri phuphi mohtarma (aawaz sey) roney lagi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is par na ro. tumharey uthaney tak farishton ney barabar us ko apney paron key sath saya kiye rakha."
1847,"Hazrat Jabir bin Ateek Raziallahu anhuma ney bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Abdullah bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki bimar pursi key liye tashrif laye to unhein maut ki be-hoshi mein paya. aap ney unhein pukara magar wo jawab na dey sakey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (انا للہ و انا الیہ راجعون) padha aur farmaya : aey Abu Rabia ! hum tumharey mamley mein be-bas hain (warna hum to tumhari zindagi key khuwaish-mand hain). ye sun kar aurten cheekh pukar karney lagin. Jabir bin Ateek unhein chup karaney lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : rehney do lekin jab wajib ho jaey to phir koi aurat (aawaz sey) na roey. logon ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! wajib hona kya hai? aap ney farmaya : maut. un ki beti kehney lagi : abba jaan ! mujhey to ummid thi ke aap shaheed hongey kyonkey aap ney apna samane jihad tayyar kar rakha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : yaqinan Allah Taala ney un ki niyat key mutabiq unka sawab likh diya hai. (phir haaziriin sey puchha : ) tum shahadat kisey samajhtey ho? unhoney kaha : Allah Taala key raastey mein maarey jana. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya, Allah key raastey mein maarey janey key ilawa bhi shahadat ki saat soorten hain : taaoon sey mar janey wala shaheed hai. pet ki takleef sey mar janey wala bhi shaheed hai. gharq ho kar marney wala bhi shaheed hai. dabb kar mar janey wala bhi shaheed hai. andruni phodey (cancer aur sartaan waghera) sey mar janey wala bhi shaheed hai. aag mein jal kar mar janey wala bhi shaheed hai aur zachgi key doran mein mar janey wali aurat bhi shaheed hai."
1848,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jab Zaid bin Harisa, Jafar bin Abi Talib aur Abdullah bin Rawaaha Raziallahu anhum ki (ghazwaey-mautaa mein) shahadat ki khabar aai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (masjid mein) beth gaey. aap key chehrey mubarak par gham key aasaar mojud  they. main darwazey ki jhuri (darz) sey dekh rahi thi ke eik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : Jafar (key ghar) ki aurten (oonchi oonchi) ro rahi hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ja unhein rok. wo chala gaya, phir (kuchh der baad) aa gaya aur kehney laga : mainey unhein roka hai lekin wo ruk nahin rahin. aap ney farmaya : ja aur unhein rok. wo chala gaya, phir aa gaya aur kehney laga : mainey phir roka hai magar wo phir bhi baaz nahin aayin. aap ney farmaya : ja phir unkey munh mein mitti dal dey. Hazrat Aaisha ney farmaya : mainey (ghussey sey) kaha : Allah tujhey zaleel kerey. Allah ki qism ! na to to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko sukoon sey bethney deta hai aur na to kuchh kar sakta hai."
1849,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maiyat ko uskey ghar walon key is par roney sey azab diya jata hai."
1850,Hazrat Muhammad bin Sirin (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain : Hazrat Imran bin Husain Raziallahu anhuma key paas ye baat zikr ki gaee ke maiyat ko zinda logon key roney sey azab hota hai to Imran (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney irshad farmaai hai.
1851,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maiyat ko uskey ghar walon key is par roney ki wajeh sey azab diya jata hai."
1852,Hazrat Qais bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ney (apni wafat sey pehley) farmaya : mujh par nauha na karna kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par nauha nahin kya gaya. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai.
1853,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney musalman honey wali aurton sey (zabani) baiat li to un sey ehad liya ke wo nauha nahin kerengi. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kuchh aurton ney daurey jahiliyat mein nauhey mein hamari madad ki thi to kya hum un ki madad kar lein? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Islam mein aisi madad karna jayez nahin."
1854,Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai ke maiyat par nauha karney sey us ko qabr mein azab diya jata hai.
1855,"Hazrat Imran bin Husein Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain ke maiyat ko ghar walon key nauha karney ki wajeh sey azab diya jata hai. eik aadmi ney un sey kaha : aap bataeyn eik aadmi khuraasaan mein mar gaya aur uskey ghar walon ney is par yahan nauha kiya, to kya usey wahan ghar walon key nauha karney ki wajeh sey azab hoga? (yani aisa nahin ho sakta) Hazrat Imran ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sach farmaya hai, tu hi ghalat kehta hai."
1856,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba maiyat ko uskey ghar walon key roney ki wajeh sey azab diya jata hai. ye baat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey zikr ki gaee to farmaney lagin : ibne-Umar ko ghalati lag gaee. baat ye thi ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik qabr key paas sey guzrey they. aap ney farmaya is qabr waley ko (apney gunahon ki wajeh sey) azab ho raha hai aur uskey ghar waley is par ro rahey hain. phir Hazrat Aaisha ney ye aayat padhi : (لا تزر وازرۃ وزر اخری),''koi bojh uthaney wala kisi ka bojh nahin uthaeyga. (dekhiye hadees : 1851)"
1857,"Hazrat Umra (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key samney zikr kiya gaya ke Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : bilashuba maiyat ko zinda logon key is par roney ki wajeh sey azab diya jata hai. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Allah Taala Abu Abdur-Rehman (ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma) ko maaf farmaey, unhoney jhoot nahin bola lekin wo bhool gaey ya unhein ghalati lag gaee, haqiqat ye hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik faut shuda Yahudi aurat (key ghar) key paas sey guzrey jis par roya ja raha tha to aap ney farmaya : ye log is par ro rahey hain jabkey usey (apney kufr aur gunahon ki bina par) azab diya ja raha hai."
1858,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney to ye farmaya tha : beshak Allah Taala kafir key liye uskey ghar walon key is par baaz (makhsus qism key) roney ki wajeh sey azab mein izafa kar deta hai.
1859,"Hazrat ibne Abi Muleka ney kaha : jab (Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti ) Ummey Aban faut huin to main bhi logon key sath (unkey ghar) gaya. mujhey Hazrat Abdullah bin umr aur Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhum key qarib bethney ka muqa mila. aurten roney lagin to Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya aap unhein roney sey nahin roktey? bilashuba mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : maiyat ko uskey ghar walon key is par baaz (makhsus qisam key) roney ki wajeh sey azab hota hai. Hazrat ibne-Abbas farmaney lagey : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aisi hi baat kehtey they. main eik dafa Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key sath safar mein nikla yahan tak ke jab hum bedaa key maqam par pahunchey to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik darkht key nichey eik qafila dekha to farmaya : jaao, dekho ye qafiley waley kon hain? main gaya to wo Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) aur unkey ghar waley they. mainey wapis aa kar bataya : Ameerul-momineen ! wo Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) aur unkey ghar waley hain. farmaya : Suheb ko merey paas lao, phir hum jab Madina Munawra aaye to (chand din baad) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) par qaatilaana hamla ho gaya. Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) unkey paas beth kar roney lagey aur kehney lagey : haaye merey piyarey bhai ! haaye merey piyarey bhai ! Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Suheb ! na ro, kyonkey mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : maiyat ko uskey ghar walon key is par baaz (makhsus qisam key) roney ki bina par azab diya jata hai. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey ye baat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey zikr ki to farmaney lagin : Allah ki qism ! tum ye hadees kisi jhootey aur jhoot ki taraf mansub ashkhaas sey bayan nahin kartey lekin sunney mein ghalati lag jati hai. tumharey liye Quran Majeed mein iska hal mojud hai (لا تزر وازرۃ وزر اخری),''koi bojh uthaney wala kisi dusrey ka bojh nahin uthaeyga'' lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney yun farmaya tha : Allah Taala kafir key azab mein uskey ghar walon key is par roney ki wajeh sey izafa farmata hai."
1860,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki aal mein sey eik shakhsiyat faut ho gaee to aurten ikhatti ho kar roney lagin. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) uth kar unhein rokney aur in ko muntashir karney lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umr ! rehney do. aakhon sey aansoo gira hi kartey hain, dil mein sadma hota hi hai aur abhi wafat taza hai."
1861,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo shakhs hum mein sey nahin jo (kisi musibat par) rukhsaaron par thappad maarta hai, gireban phaadta hai ya daure jahiliyat ki pukar pukarta (nauha karta) hai. ye alfaz (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) key ustaad) Ali (bin Khashram) ney bayan kiye hain jabkey (Imam sahab key dusrey ustaad Husain (bin Ismail (بدعاء ) ki bajaey ) (بدعوی) key alfaz bayan kartey hain. (jabkey maana aur mafhoom eik hi hai, sirf alfaz ka farq hai.)"
1862,"Hazrat Safwan bin Muharriz bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) be-hosh ho gaey to ghar waley un par roney lag gaey. (hosh mein aaney key baad) unhoney farmaya : main tumharey is kaam sey bari hone ka izhar karta hun jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamarey samney is sey bari hone ka aelaankiya tha : wo shakhs hum mein sey nahin jo (musibat key moqey par) baal mundwaaey, kapdey phaadey aur cheekh aur pukar karey."
1863,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo shakhs hum mein sey nahin jo (musibat key waqt) rukhsaar peetey, gireban phaadey aur jaahiliyat jaisi cheekh aur pukar kerey."
1864,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid aur Abu-Barda farmatey hain ke : jab Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ki takleef (marzul-maut mein) badh gaee to un ki biwi roti chalaati hui aai, wo hosh mein aaye to farmaney lagey : kya main tujhey bata na dun ke main har shakhs sey bari hun jis sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) laa-taaluq hain? Hazrat Abu-Musa apni biwi mohtarma ko ye hadees bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main us shakhs sey laa-taaluq hun jisney (musibat key moqe par bator sog) baal mundwaaey, kapdey phaadey ya cheekh aur pukar ki."
1865,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo shakhs hum mein sey nahin jo (musibat key waqt) rukhsaar peetey, gireban phaadey aur jahiliyat ki pukar pukarey."
1866,"Hazrat Yazid bin Aus sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) be-hosh ho gaey to un ki eik laundi (jo unkey bachon ki maa bhi thi) roney lagi. jab wo hosh mein aaye to us sey farmaya : kya tujhey wo baat nahin pahunchi jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaai hai? (baad mein) hamney us laundi sey puchha to usney bataya ke (unhoney farmaya tha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo shakhs hum mein sey nahin jo (musibat key moqe par) cheekhey chillaey, baal moondey aur kapdey phaadey."
1867,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo shakhs hum mein sey nahin jo (sog mein) baal moondey, cheekhey chillaey ya kapdey phaadey."
1868,"Hazrat Qarsaa ney kaha : jab Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko takleef ziyada ho gaee to un ki eik biwi mohtarma roney lagin, Hazrat Abu-Musa ney farmaya : kya tujhey pataa nahin ke is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kya farmaya hai? wo kehney lagin, kyon nahin? phir wo chup ho gaeen, baad mein un sey puchha gaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka wo farman kya tha? wo kehney lagin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us shakhs par lanat ki hai jo (sog ki bina par) baal moondey ya cheekhey chillaey ya kapdey phaadey."
1869,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti (Hazrat Zainab (Raziallahu anha)) ney aap ko pegham bheja ke mera beta qaribul-wafaat hai, aap tashrif laaeyn, aap ney ju-hi pegham bheja, salam kaha aur farmaya : Allah hi ka hai jo us ney ley liya aur usi ka hai jo us ney dey rakha tha, aur Allah Taala key yahaan har chiz ki muddat muqarrar hai, lihaza usey chahiye ke wo sabr karey aur (agar koi musibat pahunchey to) sawab talab karney ki niyat kerey. aap ki beti ney dobara pegham bheja aur aap ko qism di ke aap zarur tashrif laaeyn. aap uthey jabkey aap key sath hazraat Saad bin Ibaada, Muaz bin Jabal, Ubai bin Kaab, Zaid bin Sabit aur bahut sey dusrey sahaba Raziallahu anhu bhi they. (jab aap pahunchey to) bachcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pakdaayaa gaya. bachchey ka saans ukhad raha tha. aap ki aakhon sey aansoo bahney lagey. Hazrat Saad ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ye rehmat hai jo Allah Taala apney bandon key dilon mein paida karta hai aur Allah Taala apney bandon mein sey unhi par reham farmata hai jo dusron par reham kartey hain."
1870,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sabr pehli chot key waqt hai."
1871,"Hazrat Qurra Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya, uskey sath us ka eik beta tha. aap ney us aadmi sey farmaya : kya to is sey mohabbat karta hai? us ney kaha : Allah Taala aap sey wesi hi mohabbat farmaai jaisi main is sey rakhta hun (yani mujhey is sey inteha darjey ki mohabbat hai). huwa yun ke wo bachcha faut ho gaya. aap ney jab kaee din us shakhs ko na dekha to uskey barey mein puchha. (aap ko bataya gaya to aap ney usey bulaya, wo aaya to) aap ney farmaya : kya tujhey ye baat achchhi nahin lagti ke to (qiyamat key din) jannat key jis darwazey par bhi jaey, wahan usey paey, wo bhaagtaa huwa terey liye darwaza kholey?"
1872,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib ney Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Husain ko unkey eik faut honey waley betey ki ta'ziyat kartey huye (khat) likha ke mainey apney walid mohtaram (Hazrat Shoaib) ko apney dada Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas Raziallahu anhuma ki riwayat sey ye bayan farmatey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Allah Taala apney momin bandey key jigar goshey ko apney paas bula ley, aur wo is par sabr karey aur Allah Taala sey us (musibat key badley) sawab talab karey aur wohi baat munh sey nikaley jis ka Allah Taala ney usey hukm diya hai to Allah Taala jannat sey kam koi badla uskey liye pasand nahin farmata."
1873,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apni aulad mein sey (faut honey waley) teen bachchon ki wafat par sabr karey aur sawab talab kerey. wo jannat mein jaeyga. eik aurat khadi ho kar kehney lagi : agar do bachchey hon to? aap ney farmaya : do hon, tab bhi. (baad mein) us aurat ney kaha : kaash! main (eik bachcha) bhi keh deti."
1874,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis musalman key teen nabaligh bachchey faut ho jaeyn (phir wo un par sabr kerey) to Allah Taala un (bachchon) par apni rehmat ziyada honey key baais us (musalman) ko jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga."
1875,"Hazrat Sasaa bin Muawiya ney kaha : main Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey mila aur arz kiya : mujhey koi hadees bayan farmaain ! farmaya : achchaa, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo bhi do musalman (maa, baap) hon aur unkey teen nabaligh bachchey faut ho jaaeyn to Allah Taala un (bachchon) par apni rehmat ziyada honey ki wajeh sey un dono (waliden) key gunah bhi maaf farma deyga."
1876,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis musalman shakhs key teen bachchey faut ho jaeyn (aur wo un par sabr kerey) to usey aag nahin chhueygi magar qism puri karney key liye."
1877,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jin musalman maa baap key teen nabaligh bachchey faut ho jaeyn, Allah Taala un (bachchon) par apni rehmat ziyada honey ki wajeh sey unkey maa baap ko bhi jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga. bachchon sey kaha jaaeyga : tum jannat mein dakhil ho jaao. wo kahengey : hum tab jaeyngey jab hamarey maa baap bhi jannat mein jaeyn to farmaya jaeyga : tum aur tumharey maa baap sab jannat mein dakhil ho jaao."
1878,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas apney mareez betey ko ley kar aai aur kehney lagi : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey is (ki maut) ka khatra hai jabkey pehley bhi merey teen bachchey mar chukey hain to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tu ney aag sey (bachney key liye) mazbut rukawat tayyar kar li hai.
1879,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Zaid aur Hazrat Jafar Raziallahu anhuma ki wafat ki ittilaa un ki khabar aaney sey pehley hi (ba-zariya ""wahi"") farma di thi. jab aap ney ittilaa farmaee to aap ki aakhon sey aansoo beh rahey they."
1880,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Habsha key badshah Najaashi (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ki wafat ki ittilaa (ba-zariya ""wahi"") usi din dey di thi jis din wo faut huye aur farmaya : apney bhai key liye bakhshish ki dua karo."
1881,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke : eik dafa hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath chaley ja rahey they ke aap ney eik aurat ko dekha. wo aurat ye nahin samajhti thi ke aap ney usey pehchan liya hai. jab aap raastey key darmiyan mein pahunchey to ruk gaey yahan tak ke wo aurat aap key qarib pahunch gaee to pataa chala ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) hain. aap ney un sey kaha : Fatima ! ghar sey kaisey nikli ? unhoney kaha : main falan maiyat key ghar walon key paas gaee thi. mainey un sey izhare-afsos kiya aur sabr ki talqin ki aur tasalli di. aap ney farmaya : kahin aap unkey sath qadaa qabristaan main to nahin gaeen? unhoney kaha : Allah ki panah ke main wahan jati jabkey mainey aap ko is barey mein badey sakht alfaz farmatey suna hai. aap ney farmaya : agar to unkey sath qabristaan jati to jannat ko dekh bhi na sakti (dakhil hona to door ki baat hai) yahan tak ke terey walid key dada (Abdul-Muttalib) usey dekhen. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) farmatey hain Rabeea zaeef hai.
1882,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya Ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni saahibzaadi ki wafat key waqt hamarey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : isey teen martaba ya paanch martaba ya is sey ziyada martaba, agar zarurat ho to, pani aur beri key patton sey ghusl do aur aakhiri martaba kaafur dal do ya thoda sa kaafur shamil kar do aur farigh ho kar mujhey ittilaa dena. chunanche hamney farigh ho kar aap ko ittilaa di to aap ney hamein apna tehband diya aur farmaya : isey uskey badan par lapet do."
1883,"Hazrat Umme-Qais (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mera beta faut ho gaya. mujhey is par sakht sadma huwa. mainey ghusl deney waley sey kaha : merey betey ko thandey pani sey ghusl na dena ke to usey maar dey. (mera bhai) Hazrat Ukaasha bin Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaya aur meri ye baat aap ko batai, aap muskuraaey aur farmaya : kya kaha us ney? uski umr lambi ho. hum koi aur aurat aisi nahin jantey jisey us jaisi umr di gaee ho."
1884,Hazrat Hafsa binte Sirin bayan karti hain ke hamein Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) (aap key daur ki ghaasila) ney bayan farmaya : ghusl deney wali aurton ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti key sar ki teen mendhiyan banai thin. mainey puchha ke baalon ko khol kar phir teen mendhiyan banai thin? unhoney kaha : haan.
1885,Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni beti key ghusl key moqe par farmaya : uskey daahiney aur wuzu waley aa'zaa (ango) sey ghusl shuru karna.
1886,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki eik beti faut ho gaeen. aap ney hamein (ghusl deney key liye) bula bheja, phir farmaya : usey pani aur beri key patton sey ghusl dena aur usey teen martaba ya agar zarurat mehsus karo to paanch martaba ya saat martaba taaq dafa ghusl dena aur aakhiri dafa kuchh kaafur bhi dal lena phir jab tum farigh ho jaao to mujhey ittilaa karna. hum jab farigh huye to hamney aap ko ittilaa ki. aap ney hamari taraf apna tehband phenka aur farmaya : (kafan sey pehley) is ko is mein lapet dena. hamney unkey baalon ki teen mendhiyan kanghi sey banaeen aur unko unkey peechhey dal diya."
1887,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab hum aap ki beti ko ghusl dey rahi thin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : usey teen martaba ya paanch martaba ya us sey zayed martaba, agar zarurat mehsus karo, to pani aur beri key patton sey ghusl do aur aakhiri martaba thoda sa kaafur bhi shamil kar do, phir jab tum farigh ho to mujhey ittilaa kar dena. chunanche jab hamney farigh ho kar aap ko ittilaa di to aap ney apna tehband hamari taraf phenka aur farmaya is ko is mein lapet kar phir kafan dena."
1888,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki eik beti faut ho gaeen. aap ney hamein bula bheja aur farmaya : usey teen martaba ya paanch martaba ya us sey zayed dafa, agar zarurat mehsus karo to, pani aur beri sey ghusl dena. aur aakhiri dafa kaafur dal dena ya thoda sa kaafur (pani mein) mila lena, phir jab tum farigh ho to mujhey ittilaa karna. jab hum farigh huin to hamney aap ko ittilaa ki. aap ney hamari taraf apna tehband phenka aur farmaya : ( kafan deney sey pehley) is mein us ko lapet dena."
1889,Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey is jaisi riwayat aati hai magar is mein ye alfaz hain ke aap ney farmaya : teen martaba ya paanch martaba ya saat martaba ya us sey ziyada martaba agar tum zarurat mehsus karo to ghusl do.
1890,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki eik beti faut ho gaeen to aap ney hamein unhein ghusl deney ka hukm diya aur farmaya : usey teen martaba ya paanch martaba ya saat martaba ya us sey bhi zayed dafa, agar zarurat mehsus karo to ghusl dena. mainey kaha : ji taaq? aap ney farmaya : haan. aur aakhiri dafa kaafur dal lena. ya kuchh kaafur (pani mein) mila lena, phir jab farigh hona to mujhey ittilaa karna. jab hum (ghusl sey) farigh ho gaeen to hamney aap ko ittilaa ki. aap ney apna tehband hamein diya aur farmaya : (sab sey pehley) usey is mein lapeten."
1891,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye jabkey hum aap ki beti ko ghusl dey rahi thin. aap ney farmaya : usey teen martaba ya paanch martaba ya is sey zayed martaba agar zarurat mehsus karo to, pani aur beri (key patton) sey ghusl dena aur aakhiri dafa kaafur ya kuchh kaafur dal lena, phir jab tum farigh ho to mujhey ittilaa karna. jab hum farigh huin to hamney aap ko ittilaa ki. aap ney apna tehband hamari taraf phenka aur farmaya is ko is mein lapet dena. (Hadees key raawi) Ayub bayan kartey hain ke Hafsa binte Sirin ney kaha : usey teen martaba ya paanch martaba ya saat martaba ghusl dena. aur Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : hamney un ki teen mendhiyan kanghi sey bana den."
1892,Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke hamney unkey sar key baalon ki teen mendhiyan bana den.
1893,Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke hamney unkey sar (key baalon) ki teen mendhiyan bana den.
1894,"Hazrat Ayub bin Abi Temeeya sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Muhammad bin Sirin ko kehtey huye suna ke Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) jo ke ansaar mein sey thin, apney eik betey ki khabar leney key liye aai thin magar usey (zinda) na paya. unhoney bayan farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye jabkey hum aap ki beti ko ghusl dey rahi thin. aap ney farmaya : isey teen martaba ya paanch martaba ya is sey zayed martaba, agar zarurat samjho to, pani aur beri key patton sey ghusl do aur aakhiri martaba kaafur bhi dal do ya thoda sa kaafur shamil kar do. aur jab ghusl sey farigh ho to mujhey ittilaa karna. jab hum farigh huin (aur hamney aap ko ittilaa ki) to aap ney hamari taraf apna tehband phenka aur farmaya : usey is mein lapet do. is sey zayed kuchh na farmaya. (Hadees key raawi)  Ayub ney kaha : main nahin janta ke ye aap ki kon si beti thin? (Hadees key raawi) ibne Juraij kehtey ke mainey (Ayub bin Abi Temeeyaa sey) puchha : aap key farman (أشعرنھا إیاہ) ka matlab kya hai? kya isey us ka izaar banaya jaeyga? unhoney farmaya : mera khayal hai aap ka matlab ye tha ke usey is mein lapet do."
1895,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki eik beti faut ho gaeen, aap ney farmaya : isey teen martaba ya paanch martaba ya is sey zayed martaba, agar zarurat samjho to, ghusl do. aur usey pani aur beri (key patton) sey ghusl do aur aakhiri martaba kaafur dal do ya kuchh kaafur dalo. jab tum farigh ho to mujhey ittilaa karna. hamney aap ko ittilaa ki to aap ney apna tehband hamari taraf phenka aur farmaya : uskey badan par isey lapet do."
1896,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khutba irshad farmaya to aap ney apney eik sahabi ka zikr farmaya jo faut ho gaya tha aur usey raaton raat dafn kar diya gaya tha aur naqis kafan pehnaya gaya tha, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi maiyat ko raat key waqt dafn karney sey mana farma diya magar ye ke intehai majburi aur laachaari ho, isi ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi par apney kisi bhai (rishtey-daar) key kafan dafn ki zimmey-daari aa padey to wo uskey liye achchha kafan tayyar karey."
1897,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : safed kapdey pehnaa karo kyonkey ye ziyada saaf suthrey aur umda hotey hain aur apney faut honey walon ko bhi inhi mein kafan diya karo."
1898,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko (Yamenke ilaaqey ki) sehwal basti key baney huye teen safed kapdon mein kafan diya gaya.
1899,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko sehwal basti key baney huye teen safed kapdon mein kafan diya gaya jin mein koi qamis ya pagdi na thi.
1900,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko Yamen key baney huye teen safed suti kapdon mein kafnaaya gaya, un mein koi qamis ya pagdi na thi. Hazrat Aaisha sey zikr kiya gaya ke baaz log kehtey hain ke do kapdey they aur teesri dhaari daar chadar thi. unhoney farmaya : chadar (dhaari daar) laee to gaee thi magar ghusl aur kafan deney walon ney wapis kar di thi, is mein aap ko kafan nahin diya."
1901,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke jab Abdullah bin Abi (munafiq ka sardar) mar gaya to uskey betey (Abdullah) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur guzarish ki ke mujhey apni qamis mubarak ata farmaain taake main apney baap ko is mein kafan dun. aap us ka janaza bhi padhiye aur uskey liye bakhshish ki dua bhi kijiye. aap ney unhein qamis dey di aur farmaya : jab tum ghusl aur kafan sey farigh ho to mujhey ittilaa karna, main us ka janaza padhunga. (jab aap janaazey par pahunchey to) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap ko apni taraf mutawajjeh kiya aur guzarish ki ke kya Allah Taala ney aap ko munafiq ka janaza padhney sey roka nahin? aap ney farmaya : (nahin) mujhey do chizon mein ikhtiyar diya gaya hai ke un (munafiq) key liye bakhshish talab karu ya na karu, Allah unhein maaf nahin farmaeyga. phir aap ney janaza padh diya. baad mein Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaari :(ولا تصل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) احد … … … … wala تقم Ali (Raziallahu anhu) قبرہ), ''in munafiq mein sey koi mar jaey to kabhi bhi us ka janaza na padhen aur na uski qabr par khadey hon.'' phir aap ney munafiq ka janaza padhna chhod diya."
1902,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Abdullah bin Abi ki qabr par tashrif laye jabkey usey lahad mein rakha ja chuka tha, aap qabr par khadey huye aur usey nikalney ka hukm diya. usey (qabr sey) nikala gaya, phir aap ney usey apney ghutnon par rakha aur usey apni qamis pahnaai aur uskey munh mein (ya uskey jism par) apna lu'aab mubarak dala. Allah Taala khub janta hai (hikmat kya thi)?"
1903,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Madina mein (qaid) they to (un ki qamis phati hui thi, lihaza) ansaar ney unkey liye koi kapda talash kiya jo unhein pehna saken magar Abdullah bin Abi ki qamis key ilawa koi qamis un par sahih na aati thi (kyonkey wo qad-aawar they aur wo bhi qad aawar tha) aakhir unhoney wohi in ko pehna di."
1904,"Hazrat Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath hijrat ki to hum sirf Allah Taala ki raza mandi key Talib they, lihaza hamara sawab Allah Taala ney apney zimmey ley liya. hum mein sey kuchh to is haalat mein faut huye ke unhoney apney ajr aur sawab ka kuchh bhi hissa duniya mein wasul na kiya tha. aisey mukhlison mein sey eik Hazrat Musab bin Umer (Raziallahu anhu) they jo jange-uhad mein shaheed huye. hamein in ko kafan deney key liye sirf eik chadar mili, wo bhi itni (chhoti thi) ke jab hum unka sar dhaanptey to unkey paaun nangey ho jatey they aur jab hum unkey paaun dhaanptey they to unka sar nangaa ho jata tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey farmaya ke hum us sey unka sar dhanp den aur paaun par ghaas dal den. aur hum mein sey kuchh aisey log bhi hain ke jinkey liye unkey sawab ka phal is duniya mein bhi pak kar tayyar ho gaya. wo us ko tod tod kar kha rahey hain. hadees key ye alfaz Ismail bin Masood raawi key bayan karda hain."
1905,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Mohrim (ehraam waley) ko uskey unhi do kapdon mein ghusl do jin mein us ney ehraam baandha tha. aur usey pani aur beri (key patton) sey ghusl do. us ko unhi do kapdon mein kafan do aur usey khushbu na lagao aur na us ka sar dhaanpo kyonkey wo qiyamat key din ehraam ki haalat mein uthaya jaeyga."
1906,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : behtareen khushbu kastoori hai."
1907,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kastoori tumhari behtareen khushbu hai."
1908,"Hazrat Abu-Umama bin Sahal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke eik miskeen aurat bimar ho gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko uski bimari ki khabar di gaee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) miskeen logon ki bimar pursi aur khabar geeri farmaya kartey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab ye faut ho jaey to mujhey ittilaa karna. us ka janaza raat ko ley jaya gaya aur sahaba ney pasand na kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko jagaaen. jab subah hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko is waqiey ki khabar di gaee. aap ney farmaya : mainey tumhein kaha nahin tha ke mujhey uski ittilaa dena? Sahaba ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamney raat key waqt aap ko jagaana munasib na samjha, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) qabristaan ki taraf chaley aur uski qabr par logon ki safen banain aur chaar takbeeren kahin. (yani janaza padha.)"
1909,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jab nek shakhs charpai par rakha jata hai to wo kehta hai : mujhey jaldi ley chalo, mujhey jaldi ley chalo. aur jab bura aadmi charpai par rakha jata hai to wo kehta hai : afsos ! mujhey kahan ley ja rahey ho?"
1910,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab maiyat ko charpai par rakha jata hai aur log usey apney kandhon par utha letey hain to agar wo nek ho to kehta hai : mujhey jaldi ley chalo, mujhey jaldi ley chalo. aur agar wo nek nahin to kehta hai : haaye afsos ! mujhey kahan ley ja rahey ho? uski aawaz ko insan key ilawa har chiz sunti hai agar insan sun ley to be-hosh ho jaey."
1911,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, aur wo is riwayat ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunchatey they, ke aap ney farmaya : janaza jaldi ley kar chalo. agar wo nek hai to tum usey khair ki taraf ley ja rahey ho aur agar wo nek nahin to tum eik shar ko apni gardanon sey utaar rahey ho."
1912,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : maiyat ko jaldi ley jaao kyonkey agar wo nek hai to tum usey khair ki taraf jaldi ley ja rahey ho aur agar wo nek nahin to tum eik shar ko apni gardanon sey utaar rahey ho.
1913,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Joshan farmatey hain ke main Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura key janaazey mein hazir huwa. Ziyad (governer Basra) chaarpai key aagey aagey chalney laga. Hazrat Abdur-Rehman key gharelu rishtey-daar aur unkey ghulam (charpai key aagey) charpai ki taraf munh kar key ultey paaun chalney lagey. aur wo (janaza uthaney walon ko) kehtey they : aahista aahista chalo. Allah Taala tumhari neki mein barkat farmaey. to is tarah wo goya raing-raing kar (yani bahut aahista) chal rahey they yahan tak ke jab hum raastey mein marbad maqam par pahunchey to Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) khachchar par sawar peechhey sey hamein aa miley. jab unhoney un logon ko aisa kartey dekha to un ki taraf khachchar ko daudaayaa aur un ki taraf koda lehraaya aur farmaya : raasta chhod do. (yani maiyat key aagey sey hat jaao) mujhey qism hai us zaat ki jisney Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key chehre anwar ko izzat di hai ! mujhey achchhi tarah yad hai ke hum to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein maiyat ko utha kar tez tez chaltey they, phir (ye baat sun kar) sab log mutmain ho gaey."
1914,Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Allah ki qism ! mujhey khub yad hai ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein maiyat ko ley kar tez tez chaltey they. hadees key mazkura alfaz Haisham key hain (na ke Ismail key).
1915,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab janaza tumharey paas sey guzrey to khadey ho jaao, phir jo shakhs janaazey key sath jaey, wo janaza (zameen par) rakhey janey tak na bethey."
1916,"Hazrat Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi janaza (aata huwa) dekhey aur us ney janaazey key sath na jana ho to (kam se kam) khada ho jaey yahan tak ke janaza us sey aagey guzar jaey ya guzarney sey pehley zamin par rakh diya jaey."
1917,"Hazrat Aamir bin Rabeea Adwi (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum janaza (aata) dekho to khadey ho jaao yahan tak ke janaza tum sey aagey guzar jaey ya ( zamin par) rakh diya jaey."
1918,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum janaza (aata) dekho to khadey ho jaao jo shakhs janaazey key sath jaey wo na bethey yahan tak ke janaza ( zamin par) rakh diya jaey."
1919,Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Abu-Saeed Raziallahu anhuma dono ney farmaya : hamney to kabhi nahin dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kisi janaazey key sath tashrif farma hon aur janaza zamin par rakhey janey sey pehley beth gaey hon.
1920,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey eik janaza ley kar guzrey to aap khadey ho gaey. Amr (bin Ali ki riwayat mein yun hai, unhon) ney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey eik janaza guzra to aap khadey ho gaey."
1921,"Hazrat Yazid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke (eik dafa) hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath bethey they ke eik janaza aata nazar aaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uth khadey huye aur jo log aap key paas they wo bhi uth khadey huye, phir sab khadey rahey yahan tak ke janaza aagey guzar gaya."
1922,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Lailaa bayan kartey hain ke hazraat Sahal bin Hanif aur Qais bin Saad bin Ubada Raziallahu anhuma qaadsiya maqam par they ke eik janaza guzra. wo dono khadey ho gaey. un sey kaha gaya : ye janaza to is ilaqey walon (yani zimmi kafiron) ka hai? to un dono ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey eik janaza guzra to aap khadey ho gaey. aap sey kaha gaya : ye to eik Yahudi ka janaza hai ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya ye insani jaan nahin thi?
1923,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain ke hamarey paas sey eik janaza guzra to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho gaey. hum bhi aap key sath khadey ho gaey. (baad mein) mainey aap sey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye to eik Yahudi aurat ka janaza tha ! aap ney farmaya : maut ghabrahat wali chiz hai lihaza jab tum koi janaza dekho to khadey ho jaao. hadees key ye alfaz Khalid raawi key bayan karda hain.
1924,"Hazrat Abu-Ma'mar bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bethey they ke eik janaza paas sey guzra. log uski wajeh sey khadey ho gaey. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ye kya hai? (tum kyon khadey huye?) logon ney kaha : ye Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ki hidayat hai. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) to sirf eik Yahudi aurat key janaazey ko dekh kar khadey huye they, uskey baad kabhi khadey nahin huye."
1925,Hazrat Muhammad bin Sirin sey riwayat hai ke hazraat Hasan bin Ali aur ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhu key paas sey eik janaza guzra. Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho gaey lekin Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma khadey na huye. Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik Yahudi key janaazey ki wajeh sey khadey nahin huye they? Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : theek hai magar phir bethey bhi rahey.
1926,Hazrat ibne Sirin (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney kaha ke hazraat Hasan bin Ali aur ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhu key paas sey eik janaza guzra. Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho gaey aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma khadey na huye. Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) janaazey ko dekh kar khadey nahin huye they? Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : khadey huye they magar phir bethey rahey.
1927,Hazrat Abu-Mujliz (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey marwi hai ke hazraat ibne-Abbas aur Hasan Raziallahu anhu  key qarib sey eik janaza guzra. un mein sey eik khadey ho gaey jabkey dusrey bethey rahey. khadey honey waley ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! main yaqinan janta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye they. bethey rehney waley ney un sey kaha. Allah ki qism ! main bhi yaqinan janta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bethey bhi rahey they.
1928,"Hazrat Muhammad Baaqar (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Hasan bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma bethey huye they ke eik janaza guzra. log khadey ho gaey yahan tak ke janaza aagey chala gaya. Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : baat itni thi ke eik Yahudi ka janaza guzra aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) janaazey key raastey mein bethey huye they. aap ney napasand farmaya ke eik Yahudi ka janaza aap key sar sey ooncha ho, is liye aap khadey ho gaey."
1929,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sahaba Raziallahu anhu eik Yahudi key janaazey ko dekh kar khadey huye jo paas sey guzra tha yahan tak ke wo nazron sey ojhal ho gaya (phir bethey).
1930,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sathi eik Yahudi key janaazey ko dekh kar khadey huye (aur phir khadey rahey ) yahan tak ke wo ojhal ho gaya.
1931,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik janaza Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey guzra to aap khadey ho gaey. aap sey kaha gaya ke ye to eik Yahudi ka janaza hai ! aap ney farmaya : hum to farishton (ki tazeem) key liye khadey huye hain.
1932,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada bin Rabai Raziallahu anhu bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey eik janaza guzra to aap ney farmaya is ney aaram pa liya ya logon ney us sey aaram pa liya. sahaba ney arz kiya : is ka kya matlab hai? aap ney farmaya : momin shakhs (maut key sath) duniya key ranj aur takleef sey aaram pa jata hai aur bad-kar shakhs (ki maut) sey log, shehar, darkht aur janwer aaram pa jatey hain."
1933,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bethey they ke eik janaza namoodaar huwa. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye aaram paney wala hai ya makhluqat ko is sey aaram mila hai. momin faut hota hai to duniya ki bimariyon, takaaleef aur musibaton sey najat pa jata hai. aur bad-kar shakhs martaa hai to us sey insan, ilaqey, darkht aur janwer najat aur aaram pa jatey hain."
1934,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik janaza guzra to uski achchhi tareef ki gaee, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : lazim ho gaee. eik aur janaza guzra to uski burai bayan ki gaee, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wajib ho gaee. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : merey maa baap aap par qurban ! eik janaza guzra, uski achchhi tareef hui to aap ney farmaya : lazim ho gaee. phir doosra janaza guzra, uski burai bayan ki gaee to aap ney phir wohi farmaya : wajib ho gaee. (kya matlab hai?) aap ney farmaya : jiski tum ney achchhi tareef ki thi uskey liye jannat lazim ho gaee aur jiski burai bayan ki uskey liye aag wajib hui. tum zamin mein Allah Taala key gawah ho."
1935,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey eik janaza ley kar guzrey. haazirin ney uski achchhi tareef ki. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wajib ho gaee. phir log eik aur janaza ley kar guzrey. haazirin ney uski burai bayan ki. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wajib ho gaee. logon ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney pehley janaazey key barey mein bhi farmaya : wajib ho gaee. aur dusrey janaazey key barey mein bhi farmaya : wajib ho gaee, '(kya matlab hai?) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : farishtey aasman mein Allah Taala key gawah hain aur tum zamin mein Allah Taala key gawah ho."
1936,"Hazrat Abul Aswad Daili (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey manqul hai ke main Madina Munawra aaya aur mujhey Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bethney ka ittifaq huwa. eik janaza guzra aur uski achchhi tareef ki gaee. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : wajib ho gaee, phir eik aur janaza guzra. uski bhi achchhi tareef ki gaee. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : wajib ho gaee, phir teesra janaza guzra to uski burai bayan ki gaee. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : wajib ho gaee. mainey arz kiya : aey Ameerul-momeneen ! kya wajib ho qaee? unhoney farmaya : mainey to isi tarah kaha hai jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : jis musalman key liye chaar aadmi nek honey ki gawahi den, Allah Taala usey jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga. hamney kaha : aur teen? farmaya : haan teen bhi. hamney kaha : aur do? aap ney farmaya : haan do bhi (yani do ki gawahi bhi moatabar hogi)."
1937,Hazrat Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas kisi faut shuda shakhs ki burai bayan ki gaee to aap ney farmaya : apney faut hone waley ka zikre-khair hi kiya karo.
1938,"Hazrat Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mardon ko bura na kaho kyonkey wo apney aemaal (ki jaza aur saza) ki taraf pahunch chukey hain."
1939,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maiyat key sath teen cheezen qabr ki taraf jati hain : uskey rishtey-daar, us ka maal aur us ka amal. do cheezen, yani rishtey-daar aur maal to wapis aa jatey hain aur eik chiz, yani us ka amal uskey paas reh jata hai."
1940,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin key momin par chhe haq hain : jab wo bimar ho jaey to uski bimar pursi kerey. jab wo faut ho jaey to (us key kafan, dafn aur janaazey mein) shareek ho, jab wo dawat dey to qubul kerey. jab wo usey miley to salam kahe, jab usey chheenk aaye to usey dua dey aur uski khair-khahi karey jab wo ghaayab ho ya mojud."
1941,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein saat chizon ka hukm diya aur saat chizon sey roka. hamein bimar ki bimar parasti kerney, chhikney waley ko dua deney, qism khaney waley ki baat ko pura karney (ba-sharte-ke wo jayez ho), mazloom ki madad kerney, har milney waley ko salam kehney, bulaney waley ki dawat qubul karney aur janaazey key sath janey ka hukm diya. aur soney ki anguthi pehanney sey, chaandi key bartan (mein khaney peeney) sey, surkh reshmi gadailon, qas basti key baney huye reshmi kapdey aur motey ya bareek har qism key resham key istimal sey mana farmaya hai."
1942,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs janaazey key sath jaey yahan tak ke us ka janaza padha jaey to usey eik qeeraat sawab milega, aur jo shakhs janaazey key sath jaey yahan tak ke usey dafn kiya jaey to usey do qeeraat sawab milega, aur qeeraat uhad pahad key barabar hai."
1943,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi janaazey key sath jaey aur (dafn sey) faraaghat tak sath rahey to usey do qeeraat sawab milega. aur jo shakhs faraaghat sey pehley wapis aa jaey to usey eik qeeraat milega."
1944,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba Raziallahu anhu sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sawar shakhs janaazey key peechhey chaley aur pedal chalney wala jahan chahey chaley (aagey ya peechhey ya barabar) aur bachey ka bhi janaza padha jaey."
1945,Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sawar janaazey key peechhey chaley aur pedal jahan chahey chaley aur nau-maulood (naw-jaat) bachchey ka janaza padha jaeyga.
1946,Hazrat Salim key walid mohtaram Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma ko janaazey key aagey chaltey dekha hai.
1947,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney bayan farmaya ke unhoney Nabi aur Abu-Bakar aur umr aur Usman Raziallahu anhum ko janaazey key aagey aagey chaltey dekha hai. riwayat key raawiyon mein sey akeley Bakr raawi ney Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahin kiya. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney kaha hai ke ye riwayat (mausul) ghalat hai aur mursal sahih hai.
1948,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke (jab Najaashi (Rahmatullahi Alaih) faut huye to) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara (Islaami) bhai (Habsha mein) faut ho gaya hai, lihaza utho aur uski namaze janaza padho."
1949,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Ansaar key bachchon mein sey eik bachchey ki maiyat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laee gaee to aap ney us ka janaza padha. mainey kaha : isey mubarak ho ye to jannat ki chidiyon mein sey eik chidiyaa hai. us ney koi burai ki na burai ki umr pai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Aaisha ! kya pata koi aur baat ho jaey? Allah Taala ney jannat banai to is mein janey waley bhi bana diye aur unhen baapon ki pushton mein paida kiya. isi tarah aag banai to is mein janey waley bhi banaey aur unhein apney baapon ki pushton mein paida kiya.
1950,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba ney zikr kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sawar janaazey key peechhey chaley, pedal jahan chahey chaley aur nau-maulood (naw-jaat) ka janaza padha jaeyga."
1951,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mushrekin ki aulad key barey mein puchha gaya (ke wo kahan jaeygi?) to aap ney farmaya : Allah hi khub janta hai ke unhoney kya kaam karney they.
1952,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mushrekin ki aulad key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala khub janta hai ke wo kya karney waley they.
1953,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mushrekin ki aulad key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : jab Allah Taala ney unhein paida farmaya to Allah Taala khub janta tha ke wo kya karney waley they.
1954,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mushrekin ki aulad key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala hi khub janta hai ke (agar wo bulooghat (jawani) ko paatey) wo kya karney waley they?
1955,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Haad sey riwayat hai ke eik erabi (dehati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap par eman ley aaya aur aap ka muttabey ban gaya, phir wo kehney laga : main to aap key sath muhaajir ban kar rahunga. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney eik sahabi ko us (key qiyam aur tuaam (khaney)) ka khayal rakhney ko kaha, phir eik jang hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ghanimat mein qaidi miley. aap ney unhein taqseem kiya to us erabi (dehati) ka hissa bhi rakha aur uskey sathiyon ko dey diya. wo unki sawari key oont churaayaa karta tha. jab wo charaa kar wapis aaya to unhoney us ka hissa usey diya. us ney kaha : ye kya hai? sathiyon ney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tujhey (ghanimat sey) hissa diya hai. us ney apna hissa liya aur usey ley kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur kehney laga : ye kya hai? aap ney farmaya : mainey tujhey tera hissa diya hai. wo kehney laga : main is ki khatir to aap ka perokar nahin bana tha main to aap ka perokar, is liye bana hun ke mujhey yahan teer lagey, aur us ney apney halaq ki taraf ishara kiya, aur main mar kar jannat mein dakhil ho jaaun. aap ney farmaya : agar to ye baat sachchay dil sey kehta hai to Allah Taala teri khahish puri farmaeyga. thodey arsey key baad wo (sahaba) phir dushman sey ladaai key liye gaey to usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas is haal mein utha kar laya gaya ke usey usi jagah teer laga huwa tha jahan us ney ishara kiya tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya ye wohi erabi (dehati) hai? logon ney kaha : ji han, aap ney farmaya is ney sachchey dil sey Allah Taala sey dua ki thi, Allah Taala ney uski khahish puri farma di. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey apni qamis mein kafan diya, phir usey aagey rakha aur is par namaz padhi. aap ki dua key ye alfaz zahir huye : aey Allah ! ye tera (sachcha) banda hai. terey raastey mein hijrat kartey huye ghar sey nikla aur shaheed ho gaya. main in baaton ka aankho dekha gawah hun."
1956,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik din (apni zindagi key aakhiri dino mein) uhad ki taraf gaey aur uhad key shuhda key liye is tarah (aah aur zaari sey (gidgidaa-kar)) duayen kin jis tarah maiyat key liye kartey they, phir wapis aa kar member par chadhey aur farmaya : main tumhara paish-rau hun. (tumhara Ameere-saman hun) aur main tumharey haq mein  (emaan aur nusrat ki ) gawahi dunga."
1957,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma ney bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (kapdon ki kami ki wajeh sey) shohdaaey uhad mein sey do-do ashkhaas ko eik-eik kapdey mein ikhatta rakhtey they, phir farmatey : in mein sey kis ko Quran ziyada yad hai? jab un mein sey kisi eik ki taraf ishara kiya jata to aap usey lahad mein (qibley ki taraf) aagey rakhtey. aur aap ney farmaya : main inkey haq mein gawahi dunga. aur aap ney in ko (kapdon aur jismon par) khoon samet dafn karney ka hukm diya. na unka janaza padha aur na unhein ghusl diya."
1958,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke banu Aslam (qabiley) ka eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur us ney zina karney ka aetraaf kiya. aap ney us sey munh mod liya. us ney phir aetraaf kiya. aap ney phir munh mod liya. us ney phir aetraaf kiya. aap ney phir munh mod liya yahan tak ke us ney apney khilaf chaar dafa gawahi di (ke mainey zina kiya hai) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey jaanon to nahin? us ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : to shaadi shuda hai? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney usey rajm (sangsaar) karney ka hukm diya. usey rajm (sangsaar) kiya janey laga lekin jab usey pattharon ney takleef pahunchaai to wo bhag utha, magar usey pakad liya gaya aur patthar maarey gaey yahan tak ke wo mar gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey barey mein taarifi kalimaat farmaai lekin us ka janaza nahin padha."
1959,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke juhaina ( qabiley ) ki eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aai aur kehney lagi : mainey zina kiya hai. aur wo hamila bhi thi, lihaza aap ney us aurat ko uskey wali key supurd kar diya aur farmaya : is sey husn-sulook karna. jab ye bachcha jan ley to isey merey paas ley aana. jab us ney bachcha jan liya to wo usey ley kar aaya. aap ney uskey rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm diya. uskey kapdey achchhi tarah kas kar baandh diye gaey (taake be-pardagi na ho), phir usey (aap key hukm sey) rajm (sangsaar) kiya gaya, phir aap ney us ka janaza padha. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : aap is ka janaza padhtey hain jabkey is ney to zina kiya hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! us ney aisi tauba ki hai agar wo Madiney walon mein sey sattar ashkhaas par taqseem kar di jaey to un sab ko puri aa jaey (un ki najat key liye kafi ho) aur is sey afzal tauba kya hogi ke us ney Allah Taala ko razi karney key liye apni jaan qurban kar di."
1960,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney martey waqt apney chhe ghulam azad kar diye. unkey ilawa uskey paas koi maal na tha. ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pahunchi to aap is par bahut naraz huye aur farmaya : mera irada huwa ke main us ka janaza na padhun. phir aap ney uskey ghulam bulaey, unkey teen hissey kiye, phir un mein qura dala. do ko azad farmaya aur chaar ko ghulam rakha."
1961,Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : eik aadmi ghazwae-khaibar mein faut ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum apney sathi ka janaza padh lo (main nahin padhunga) kyonkey us ney jihad key doran mein khayanat ki hai. hamney uskey saman ki talashi li to is mein yahudiyon key mungon mein sey kuchh mungey paey jo do dirham qeemat bhi nahin rakhtey they.
1962,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik Ansari shakhs ki maiyat janaazey key liye laee gaee to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum apney sathi ka janaza padh lo (main nahin padhunga) is par to qarz hai. mainey arz kiya : wo qarz merey zimmey raha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to ye zimmey-daari puri bhi kerega? mainey kaha : zarur puri karunga to aap ney uska janaza padh diya.
1963,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik janaza laya gaya. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! is ka janaza padhiye. aap ney farmaya : is par kuchh qarz to nahin? logon ney kaha : qarz hai. aap ney farmaya : ye adaegi key liye kuchh maal chhod gaya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : phir tum apney sathi ka janaza padh lo. Ansaar mein sey eik shakhs jinhein Abu-Qatada kaha jata tha, ney kaha : aap is ka janaza padhiye, is ka qarz merey zimmey hai to aap ney janaza padh diya."
1964,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aisey shakhs ka janaza nahin padhtey they jis par qarz hota tha. eik maiyat aap key paas laee gaee. aap ney puchha : kya is par qarz hai? logon ney kaha : ji haan ! is par do deenar qarz hai. aap ney farmaya : phir tum apney sathi ka janaza padh lo. Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye do deenar merey zimmey hain. aap ney janaza padh diya, phir jab Allah Taala ney apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko futoohaat din to aap ney farmaya : main har momin key liye uskey nafs sey bhi badh kar qaribi hun, lihaza jo qarz chhod jaey to uski adaegi merey (yani baitul-maal key) zimmey hai aur jo maal chhod jaey wo uskey warison ko milega."
1965,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab koi musalman faut hota aur uskey zimmey qarz hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) poochhtey : kya ye marney wala apney qarz ki adaegi key liye kuchh maal chhod gaya hai? agar log kehtey : ji han, to aap us ka janaza padhtey warna aap farmatey : tum apney sathi ka janaza padh lo. phir jab Allah Taala ney apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko futoohaat sey nawaza to aap ney farmaya : main musalmanon key liye unkey nafson sey bhi ziyada qaribi hun, lihaza jo shakhs maqrooz faut ho jaey to uskey qarz ki adaegi merey zimmey hogi aur jo shakhs maal chhod kar faut ho to wo maal uskey waarison ko milega."
1966,Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney teeron sey khudkushi kar li. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main is ka janaza nahin padhunga.
1967,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo pahad (ya kisi aur buland maqam) sey gir kar khudkushi kerey. wo jahannam ki aag mein hamesha hamesha (jahannami pahad) sey girta raheyga. aur jis shakhs ney zahar pi kar khudkushi ki to us ka zahar uskey haath mein diya jaeyga aur wo jahannam ki aag mein hamesha hamesha usey peeta raheyga. aur jo aadmi kisi tez dhaar aaley (talwaar, khanjar, chaqu ya chhuri waghera) sey khudkushi karey to us ka wo hathiyar uskey haath mein diya jaeyga aur wo hamesha hamesha jahannam ki aag mein usey apney pet mein ghonptaa raheyga."
1968,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab Abdullah bin Abi ibne Salool (munafiq) mar gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko us ka janaza padhney key liye bulaya gaya. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (janaza padhney key liye) khadey ho gaey, main jaldi sey aap key samney ja khada huwa aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aap ibne Abi ka janaza padhtey hain, halanke us ney falan falan din aisi aisi baaten ken? main (us ki shararaten) shumar karney laga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) muskuraatey rahey, aakhir farmaya : umr ! eik taraf hat jaao. jab mainey apni baat par israr kiya to aap ney farmaya : mujhey ikhtiyar diya gaya hai (ke istighfar karo ya na karo, Allah maghfirat na kerega) to mainey istighfar ko ikhtiyar kiya hai. agar mujhey ilm hota ke main sattar dafa sey zayed istighfar karun to isey maafi ho jaeygi to main yaqinan sattar dafa sey zayed bhi istighfar kar deta. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney janaza padh diya, phir wapis tashrif ley gaey. abhi thodi hi der guzri thi ke Sura bara-at ki do aayaten utrin : (ولا تصل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) احد … … … الأیۃ),''aey Nabi ! un munafiqon mein sey koi mar jaey to hergiz us ka janaza na padhen aur na un ki qabr par (dua'aey maghfirat key liye) jaeyn kyonkey unhoney Allah aur uskey Rasool ka inkar kiya aur phir usi inkar aur fisq (naafarmaani) ki haalat mein faut huye. baad mein mujhey apni is jur'at par jo mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney ki, bahut tajjub huwa kyonkey Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ziyada ilm rakhney waley hain."
1969,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Suhail ibne Baizaa (Raziallahu anhu) ka janaza masjid hi mein padha tha.
1970,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Suhail bin Baizaa (Raziallahu anhu) ka janaza masjid hi mein padha tha.
1971,"Hazrat Abu-Umama bin Sahal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : eik miskeen aurat (Madiney key muzaafat ) awaali mein bimar ho gaee to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon sey us (ki sehat) key barey mein poochhtey rehtey they, isi ke sath aap ney farmaya : agar wo faut ho jaey to usey dafn na karna yahan tak ke main us ka janaza padhun. aakhir wo faut ho gaee to log us ka janaza ley kar Isha key baad Madina Munawra mein aaye lekin unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko sotey paya. unhoney aap ko bedaar karna munasib na samjha, khud hi janaza padha aur usey Baqee gharqad mein dafn kar diya. jab subah hui to wo log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye. aap ney un sey uskey barey mein puchha to unhoney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo to dafn bhi ho chuki. hum aap key paas hazir huye they magar hamney aap ko sotey paya aur aap ko jagaana munasib na samjha. aap ney farmaya : chalo. aap chaley wo log bhi aap key sath chaley yahan tak ke unhoney aap ko uski qabr dikhai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (qabr key samney) khadey huye. wo log (aap key hukm sey) aap key peechhey saf mein khadey ho gaey. aap ney us ka janaza padhaya aur chaar takbeeren kahin."
1972,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara (Islaami) bhai Najaashi faut ho gaya hai. utho us ka janaza padho. aap khadey huye aur hamari saf bandi farmaee jaisey janaazey mein saf bandi ki jati hai, phir us ka janaza padha."
1973,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko Hazrat Najaashi (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ki wafat ki ittilaa un ki wafat hi key din farmaee thi, phir aap logon ko sath ley kar janaza gaah mein gaey. un ki saf bandi ki aur unka janaza padhaya. aur chaar takbeeren kahin."
1974,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Madina Munawra mein apney sahaba ko Najaashi (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ki wafat ki khabar di. unhoney aap key peechhey safein banaeen. aap ney janaza padhaya aur chaar takbeeren kahin. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ibne Musaiyab ka lafz main apni mansha key mutabiq samajh nahin saka.
1975,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara bhai faut ho gaya hai. utho ! us ka janaza padho. to hamney uskey janaazey mein do safen banaeen ."
1976,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jis din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Najaashi (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ka janaza padhaya main dusri saf mein tha.
1977,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, hum sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara (Islaami) bhai Najaashi faut ho gaya hai, utho us ka janaza padho. hum khadey huye aur saff-bandi ki jaisey maiyat par ki jati hai. aur us ka janaza padha jaisey maiyat ka janaza padha jata hai."
1978,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Hazrat Umme-Kaab (Raziallahu anha) ka janaza padha jo bachchey ki paidaish key waqt faut ho gaee thin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) un ki kamar key barabar khadey huye."
1979,"Hazrat Ata bin Abi Ribaah sey manqul hai ke eik aurat aur eik bachchey key janaazey ikhattey ho gaey to Hazrat Ammaar (Raziallahu anhu) ney bachchey ki maiyat ko logon ki taraf aagey rakha aur aurat ko uskey peechhey (yani qibley ki taraf) rakha aur dono ka janaza (eik hi waqt mein) padha. haazirin mein Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri, ibne-Abbas, Abu-Qatada aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhum bhi they. mainey un sey is barey mein puchha to un sab ney kaha ke yehi masnoon tariqa hai."
1980,"Hazrat Naafey sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney nau maiyaton ka ikhatta janaza padha. mardon ko Imam ki janib rakha aur aurton ko qibley ki janib aur un sab ko eik seedh mein rakha. aur (isi tarah) Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Hazrat ummey Kulsoom binte Ali aur unkey betey jin ka naam Zaid tha, ko ikhatta rakha gaya. us waqt Imam Saeed bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) they. haazirin mein ibne-Umar, Abu-Huraira, Abu-Saeed aur Abu-Qatada Raziallahu anhum shamil they. bachchey ko Imam ki janib rakha gaya. eik aadmi ney kaha ke mainey is ko durust na samjha to mainey hazraat ibne-Abbas, Abu-Huraira, Abu-Saeed aur Abu-Qatada Raziallahu anhum ki taraf dekha aur kaha : ye kya hai? un sab ney kaha : yehi masnoon tariqa hai."
1981,Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ummey falan (Umme-Kaab (Raziallahu anha)) ka janaza padha jo bachchey ki paidaish key waqt faut ho gaee thin to aap unkey darmiyan mein (yani kamar key barabar) khadey huye.
1982,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko Hazrat Najaashi (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ki wafat ki ittilaa di. unhein ley kar (bahir) nikley. un ki saff-bandi ki aur janaazey mein chaar takbeeren kahin.
1983,"Hazrat Abu-Umama bin Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ilaaqa awaali main eik aurat bimar ho gaee aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bimar ki bimar pursi aur iyaadat bahut ziyada farmaya kartey they. aap ney (us aurat ki iyaadat key moqey par) farmaya : jab ye faut ho jaey to mujhey ittilaa karna. wo raat ko faut hui to unhoney (khud hi janaza padh kar) usey dafn kar diya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ittilaa na ki. subah hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey barey mein puchha to unhoney (puri soorate-haal sunaaee aur) kaha ke hamney aap ko bedaar karna munasib na samjha, phir aap uski qabr par aaye, us ka janaza padha aur chaar takbeeren kahin."
1984,"Hazrat ibn Abi Lailaa sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik maiyat ka janaza padha to is par paanch takbeeren kahin, phir farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (baaz oqaat) paanch takbeeren bhi kahi hain."
1985,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko eik maiyat ka janaza padhtey huye ye kehtey suna : (اللھم ! اغفرلہ و ارحمہ … … … وقہ عذاب القبر و عذاب النار),''aey Allah ! iskey gunah bakhsh dey aur is par reham farma. is sey darguzar farma aur isey khairiyat sey rakh. is ki achchhi mehman nawaazi farma aur is ka thikana wasee farma. aur isey pani, barf aur olon key sath dho dey aur isey ghaltiyon sey is tarah saaf farma dey jis tarah safed kapdey ko mail kuchail sey saaf kiya jata hai. aur isey iskey (dunyawi) ghar sey behtar ghar ata farma. aur iskey (dunyawi) ghar walon sey behtar ghar waley ata farma. aur iskey jodey sey behtar joda ata farma. aur isey qabr key azab aur aag key azab sey bacha.'' Hazrat Auf (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : is maiyat key liye ye (jaama') duaayen sun kar mujhey khahish hui ke kaash! main ye maiyat hota."
1986,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko eik maiyat ka janaza padhtey suna. mainey suna, aap dua mein yun farma rahey they : (اللھم ! اغفرلہ … … … ونجہ من النار),''aey Allah ! is (key gunahon) ko bakhsh dey aur is par reham farma. isey khairiyat key sath rakh aur is sey darguzar farma. is ki mehman nawaazi achchhi farma aur is ki qabr ko khula kar dey aur isey pani, barf aur olon sey dho dal. aur isey ghaltiyon (key asraat) sey is tarah pak aur saaf farma dey jis tarah tu ney safed kapdey ko mail kuchail sey saaf rakha hai. aur isey iskey ghar sey behtar ghar, iskey ghar walon sey behtar ghar waley aur iskey sathi sey behtar sathi ata farma. isey jannat mein dakhil farma aur aag sey door rakh. ya aap ney farmaya : (وأعذہ من عذاب القبر)''isey azabe-qabr sey bacha.''"
1987,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Rabeea Sulami (Raziallahu anhu) jo ke sahabiey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hain, ney Hazrat Ubaid bin Khalid Sulami (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney do aadmiyon ko aapas mein bhai bana diya. un mein sey eik shaheed ho gaya aur doosra uskey kuchh baad faut huwa. hamney us ka janaza padha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum ney (janaazey mein) uskey liye kya dua ki? sahaba ney arz kiya : hamney uskey liye ye dua ki : (اللھم ! اغفرلہ … … … الحقہ بصاحبہ),''aey Allah ! isey maaf farma. is par reham farma aur isey iskey sathi (bhai) key sath mila dey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to iskey baad uski namazein aur dusrey nek aemaal kidhar gaey? Allah ki qism ! unkey darmiyan to zamin aur aasman key maa-bain jaisa fasla hai. Amr bin memnon ney kaha : ye riwayat mujhey bahut achchhi lagi kyonkey unhon (ustaad mohtaram) ney ye riwayat (baghair wasta giraaey) mujhey bayan ki."
1988,"Hazrat Abu Ibrahim Ansari apney walid mohtaram sey bayan kartey hain unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko eik maiyat key janaazey mein yun dua kartey suna : (اللھم ! اغفر لحینا … … وکبیرنا),''aey Allah ! maaf farma dey hamarey faut shuda aur zinda ko aur hazir aur ghaayab ko aur muzakkir aur muannas (mardon aur aurton) ko aur chhotey aur badey ko.''"
1989,Hazrat Talha bin Abdullah bin Auf bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key peechhey eik maiyat ka janaza padha. unhoney Sura Fatiha aur eik aur sura padhi aur (dono) buland aawaz sey padhin yahan tak ke hamein sunai den. jab wo farigh huye to mainey unka haath pakda aur un sey is barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : ye sunnat aur haq hai.
1990,"Hazrat Talha bin Abdullah sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key peechhey eik janaza padha. mainey unhein Sura Fatiha padhtey suna. jab wo janaazey sey farigh huye to mainey unka haath pakad liya aur un sey puchha ke kya aap (janaazey mein) qirat kartey hain? unhoney farmaya : han, ye haq hai aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat hai."
1991,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke namaze-janaza mein sunnat ye hai ke pehli takbir key baad Sura Fatiha aahista padhey, phir teen takbeeren kahe aur aakhiri takbir key baad salam pher dey."
1992,Hazrat Zuhaak bin Qais dimashqi sey bhi isi qism ki (is key hum maani) riwayat aati hai.
1993,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis maiyat par musalmanon ki eik jamaat janaza padhey jo sau tak pahunchtey hun aur wo uski (bakhshish) ki sifarish karen to laziman us maiyat key haq mein un ki sifarish qubul ki jati hai. Hadees key raawi Salam bin Abu Muteea bayan kartey hain ke mainey ye riwayat Hazrat Shuaib bin Habhaab ko bayan ki to wo kehney lagey : mujhey yehi riwayat Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan ki hai."
1994,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo musalman faut ho jaey, phir is par musalmanon ki eik jamaat janaza padhey jo eik sau tak pahunchtey hon aur wo uskey liye sifarish karen to laziman un ki sifarish uskey haq mein qubul ki jati hai."
1995,"Abu Bakkaar Hukm bin Farrukh sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Mulaih ney hamein eik maiyat ka janaza padhaya. hamney samjha ke unhoney Allahu-Akbar keh diya hai lekin (achanak) unhoney hamari taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : apni safein durust aur sidhi karo. aur tumhari sifarish behtareen honi chahiye (kyonkey) mujhey Hazrat Abdullah bin Saleet ney Ummahaatul-momineen mein sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki eik biwi mohtarma Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : jis maiyat par musalmanon ki eik jamaat janaza padh dey, uskey haq mein un ki sifarish zarur qubul hogi. mainey Hazrat Abu-Mulaih sey puchha ke wo jamaat kitni ho? unhoney kaha : chaalis afrad."
1996,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi maiyat ka janaza padhey, uskey liye eik qeeraat sawab hai aur jo shakhs (janaazey key baad) intizar karta rahey yahan tak ke usey lahad mein rakh diya jaey to uskey liye do qeeraat (sawab) hai aur do qeeraat do azeem pahadon ki tarah hain."
1997,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs janaazey mein hazir ho aur janaza padhey janey tak rahey to uskey liye eik qeeraat (sawab) hai aur jo dafn kiye janey tak rahey to uskey liye do qeeraat (sawab) hai. puchha gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo qeeraat kaisey hongey? aap ney farmaya : wo azeem pahadon jaisey."
1998,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs sawab ki niyat sey kisi musalman key janaazey key sath jaey, us ka janaza padhey aur usey dafn karey to uskey liye do qeeraat hain. aur jo shakhs janaza padh kar dafn sey pehley wapis aa jaey to wo eik qeeraat (sawab) key sath palat'taa hai."
1999,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs janaazey key sath jaey, us ka janaza padhey, phir wapis aa jaey to uskey liye eik qeeraat ajr hai aur jo sath jaey, janaza padhey, phir betha rahey yahan tak ke tadfeen sey faraaghat ho to uskey liye do qeeraat ajr hai. har qeeraat uhad (pahad) sey bada hoga."
2000,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum janaza dekho to khadey ho jaao. aur jo shakhs janaazey key sath jaey, wo na bethey yahan tak ke janaza (zameen par) rakh diya jaey."
2001,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key samney janaza (zameen par) rakhey janey tak khadey rehney ka zikr kiya gaya to Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (pehley) khadey rehtey they, magar baad mein bethey rehtey they."
2002,"Hazrat Ali Raziallahu anhu bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khadey hotey dekha to hum bhi khadey rahey, phir hamney aap ko bethey dekha to hum bhi bethey rahey."
2003,Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik janaazey mein gaey. jab hum qabr key paas pahunchey to (dekha ke) qabr tayyar nahin hui thi. aap beth gaey aur hum aap key ird-gird beth gaey (baghair kisi harkat aur aawaz key) goya ke hamarey saron par perindey bethey hain.
2004,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Saulbaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney jange-uhad key shuhda key barey mein farmaya tha : unhein unkey khoon aalud jismon aur kapdon samet kafan do kyonkey jo zakham bhi Allah Taala key raastey mein laga ho, qiyamat key din uski ye haalat hogi ke rang to khoon jaisa hi hoga magar khushbu kastoori jaisi hogi."
2005,Hazrat Ubedullah bin Maiyaa sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Taaif key doran mein do musalman shaheed huye to in ko utha kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. aap ney hukm diya ke unhein wahin dafn kiya jaey jahan ye shaheed huye. (Hadees key raawi) Hazrat ibn Maiyaa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein paida huye they.
2006,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya tha ke shohdaaey-uhad ko un ki shahadat key maidan mein wapis laya jaey kyonkey un (mein sey baaz) ko Madina Munawra ley jaya gaya tha.
2007,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : shuhda (uhad ) ko un ki shahadat-gaah hi mein dafn kiya jaey.
2008,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke (jab merey walid Abu Talib faut huye to) mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey guzarish ki ke aap key gum-raah chacha faut ho gaey hain. ab unhein kon (zameen mein) chupaey (dafn kerey) ga? aap ney farmaya : jaao, apney walid ko (zameen mein) chhipaaon (dafn karo). aur merey paas wapis aaney sey pehley koi aur kaam na karna. main in ko dafnaney key baad aap key paas hazir huwa to aap ney mujhey ghusl karney ka hukm diya. mainey ghusl kiya to aap ney merey liye (sabr aur tahammul ki) dua ki lekin wo dua mujhey yad nahin."
2009,Hazrat Saad Raziallahu anhu ney (wasiyat key taur par) farmaya : merey liye lahad banana aur phir inetein laga dena jaisa ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye kiya gaya tha.
2010,Hazrat Aamir bin Saad sey riwayat hai ke jab (walid mohtaram) Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ka waqt qarib aaya to unhoney farmaya : merey liye lahad banana aur phir ineten laga dena jaisa ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye kiya gaya.
2011,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : lahad hamarey liye hai aur shaqq dusron key liye."
2012,"Hazrat Hisham bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hamney jange-uhad key din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey shikayat ki aur kaha ke har maiyat key liye alag-alag qabr khodna hamarey liye bahut mushkil hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabren khodon, gehri khodo aur achchhi tarah khodo. aur do-do, teen-teen aadmiyon ko eik qabr mein dafn kar do. logon ney puchha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum aagey kis maiyat ko rakhen? aap ney farmaya : jo ziyada Quran padha huwa ho. Hadees key raawi Hazrat Hisham ney kaha ke merey walid samet teen aadmi eik qabr mein dafn kiye gaey."
2013,"Hazrat Hisham bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jange-uhad key din bahut ziyada musalman shaheed ho gaey. (baqi bachey) logon ko bahut zakham lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (shafqqat ke sath) farmaya : khodo aur kushada khodo aur do-do, teen-teen shuda ko eik-eik qabr mein dafn kar do aur jisney Quran Majeed ziyada padha ho, usey aagey rakho."
2014,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dafn kiya gaya to aap key nichey surkh rang ki eik chadar bichhaai gaee.
2015,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke teen oqaat aisey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein un mein namaz padhney aur maiyat key dafn karney sey mana farmaya : jab suraj tulu ho raha ho yahan tak ke kuchh ooncha ho jaey. aur jab suraj nisfun'nahaar (jab suraj sar ke upar ho) par ho yahan tak ke dhal jaey. aur jab suraj ghurub honey key aen qarib ho.
2016,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khutba irshad farmaya aur apney sahaba mein sey eik shakhs ka zikr kiya jo (raat ko) faut ho gaya tha aur usey raat hi ko naqis aur ghair munasib kafan mein dafn kar diya gaya tha, lihaza Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi maiyat ko raat key waqt dafn karney sey mana farma diya siwaaey iske ke zayada majburi ho."
2017,"Hazrat Hisham bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jange-uhad key din logon ko sakht takleef pahunchi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabren khodo, kushada khodo aur do do, teen teen shuhda ko eik eik qabr mein dafn karo. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kis ko aagey (qibley ki taraf) rakhen? aap ney farmaya : jo in mein sey ziyada Quran padha huwa ho."
2018,"Hazrat Hisham bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jange-uhad mein logon ko zakhmon ki sakht takleef thi. is baat ki shikayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ki gaee. aap ney farmaya : qabren khodo, kushada khodo, aur achchhi tarah khodo, aur do do, teen teen ko eik eik qabr mein dafn karo. aur jo shakhs ziyada Quran padha huwa ho, usey aagey rakho."
2019,"Hazrat Hisham bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabren khodo aur achchhi tarah khodo aur do do, teen teen ko (ikhatta) dafn karo. aur jo shakhs Quran Majeed ziyada padha huwa ho, usey aagey rakho."
2020,"Hazrat Hisham bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jange-uhad key din merey walid shaheed ho gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabren khodo kushada khodo, aur achchhi tarah khodo aur do do, teen teen ko eik eik qabr mein dafn karo aur jisney Quran Majeed ziyada padha ho, usey aagey rakho. merey walid teen mein sey eik they (jo eik hi qabr mein dafn kiye gaey, yani unkey sath do aur aadmi dafn kiye gaey). chunkey wo (merey walid) Quran Majeed ziyada padhey huye they, lihaza unhein (qibley ki taraf) aagey rakha gaya."
2021,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Abdullah bin Abi ko qabr mein rakhey janey key baad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur usey bahar nikalney ka hukm diya, phir aap ney usey apney ghutnon par rakha aur kisi qadr apna lu'aab dahan is par dala. aur usey apni qamis pahnaai. Allah Taala hi (is ki maslihat) janta hai."
2022,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya to Abdullah bin Abi ko uski qabr sey nikala gaya, phir aap ney us ka sar apney ghutnon par rakha. aur uskey munh mein apna lu'aab dahan thookaa. usey apni qamis pahnaai aur us ka janaza padha. (in kamon ki maslihat) Allah Taala hi janta hai."
2023,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke merey walid (uhad ke shaheed) key sath qabr main eik aur shaheed bhi dafnaaey gaey they magar merey dil ko ye achchha na laga yahan tak ke mainey in ko nikal kar alehda dafn kiya.
2024,"Hazrat Yazid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik din hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath (baqeea' ki taraf) nikley to aap ney eik taza qabr dekhi. aap ney farmaya : ye qabr kaisi hai? logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye falan qabiley ki falan laundi ki qabr hai, aap ney usey pehchan liya, ye Zohar key waqt faut hui thi. aap us waqt rozey ki haalat mein dophare key waqt aaram farma rahey they. hamney is ki khatir aap ko jagaana munasib na samjha. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (qabr key rukh) khadey huye, aur apney peechhey logon ki saf banai aur aap ney chaar takbeeren kahin (yani mukammal janaza padha). phir farmaya : jab tak main tum mein mojud hun, koi shakhs bhi faut ho mujhey zarur ittilaa kiya karo kyonkey mera janaza padhna uskey liye rehmat ka sabab hai."
2025,"Hazrat Shaabi sey riwayat hai ke mujhey us sahabi ney bataya jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik alehda bani hui qabr key paas sey guzrey they, aap ney imaamat farmaee aur unhon (ibne-Abbas aur dusrey logon) ney aap key peechhey saf bandi ki. Shaabi sey puchha gaya : wo kon sey sahabi hain? unhoney kaha : Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma."
2026,Hazrat Shaabi (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey us sahabi ney khabar di jinhonney khud dekha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik alehda bani hui qabr key qarib sey guzrey to aap ney apney sahaba ki apney peechhey saf banai aur janaza padhaya. (Shaabi) puchha gaya : aap ko kis sahabi ney bayan farmaya? unhoney kaha : Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney.
2027,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aurat ki qabr par uskey dafn kiye janey key baad janaza padha.
2028,Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat ibn Dah'daah (Raziallahu anhu) key janaazey key liye nikley (pedal tashrif ley gaey). jab wapis huye to aap key paas baghair kaathi key ghodaa laya gaya. aap sawar ho gaey. hum aap key sath sath pedal chaltey rahey.
2029,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke qabr par koi imarat banai jaey ya qabr par izafa kiya jaey ya qabr ko pukhta banaya jaey. raawi Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Musa ney ye alfaz ziyada bayan kiye hain : ya is par kuchh likha jaey.
2030,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qabron ko pukhta karney ya un par imarat bananey ya un par bethney sey mana farmaya hai.
2031,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qabron ko choonaa-gach karney sey mana farmaya hai.
2032,"Hazrat Samaama bin Shafi bayan kartey hain ke hum Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Romiyon key ilaqey mein they ke hamara eik sathi faut ho gaya. to Hazrat Fazala ney hukm diya aur uski qabr humwaar kar di gaee, phir farmaney lagey : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap qabron ko humwaar karney ka hukm detey they."
2033,"Hazrat Abu-Biyaaj sey manqul hai, Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujh sey farmaya : kya main tujhey us kaam par na bhejun jis par mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney bheja tha ke to koi buland qabr na chhod magar usey humwaar kar dey aur na kisi ghar mein koi but ya tasweer chhod magar usey tod phod dey."
2034,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhein qabron ki ziyaarat sey roka tha, ab tumhein qabron ki ziyaarat karney (qabristaan mein janey) ki ijazat hai. (isi tarah) mainey tumhein teen din sey ziyada qurbani ka gosht rakhney sey mana kiya tha, ab tum rakh saktey ho, jab tak tumhara dil chahey. (isi tarah) mainey tumhein mishkeezey key ilawa kisi aur bartan mein nabeez bananey sey roka tha, ab tum har qism key bartan mein nabeez bana saktey ho, albatta nashey wala nabeez na peena."
2035,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main eik aisi majlis mein tha jis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi tashrif farma they. aap ney farmaya : mainey tumhein teen din sey zayed qurbani ka gosht khaney sey mana kiya tha lekin ab tum khaao, dusron ko khilao aur jab tak chaho rakho. (isi tarah) mainey tumhein kaha tha ke un bartanon mein nabeez na banao, yani kadu ka bartan, tarkol mila huwa bartan, khajoor ki jad ka bartan aur masam-band matka, lekin ab jis bartan mein chaho nabeez banao, albatta har nashey wali chiz sey bacho. (isi tarah) mainey tumhein qabron ki ziyaarat sey roka tha lekin ab jo qabr ki ziyaarat key liye jana chahey, jaey magar (wahan ja kar) koi ghalat baat na kaho."
2036,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni walida ki qabr dekhney gaey to khud bhi roey aur sathiyon ko bhi rulaayaa aur farmaya : mainey apney Rab taala sey ijazat talab ki thi ke main apni walida key liye bakhshish ki dua karun lekin mujhey ijazat nahin di gaee, phir mainey ijazat talab ki ke un ki qabr dekhney jaaun to mujhey ijazat dey di gaee. tum bhi qabron ki ziyaarat kiya karo kyonkey wo maut ko yad dilaati hain."
2037,"Hazrat Musaiyab (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jab Abu Talib ki wafat ka waqt aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas tashrif ley gaey. uskey paas (us waqt ) Abu-Jahal aur Abdullah bin Abi Umayya they. aap ney farmaya : aey chacha kalima (لا الہ الا اللہ ) padh ley, main isey Allah Taala key paas terey liye bator hujjat pesh karunga. Abu-Jahal aur Abdullah bin Abi Umayya usey kehney lagey : aey Abu Talib ! kya to Abdul-Muttalib key Deen ko chhod deyga? wo dono us sey is qism ki baaten kartey rahey yahan tak ke aakhiri baat jo Abu Talib ney un sey ki, wo ye thi ke main Abdul-Muttalib key Deen par hun. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : main terey liye istighfar karta rahunga b-sharte-ke mujhey roka na gaya. phir ye aayat utri : (ما کان للنبی والذین امنوآ ان یستغفروا للمشرکین),''Nabi aur eman walon key liye jayez nahin ke mushrekin key liye istighfar keren.'' aur ye aayat bhi utri : (انک لا تھدی من احببت),''aap jisey chahen raahe-raast par nahin la saktey.''"
2038,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey eik shakhs ko suna jo apney mushrik waliden key liye istighfar kar raha tha to mainey kaha : kya to unkey liye istighfar karta hai, halanke wo mushrik they? us ney kaha : kya Hazrat Ibrahim alehissalam ney apney walid key liye istighfar nahin ki thi? main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur ye baat aap sey zikr ki to ye aayat utri : (وما کان استغفار ابراھیم لابیہ الا an موعدۃ و عدھا ایاہ),''Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ka apney walid key liye istighfar karna us wadey ki bina par tha jo unhoney us sey kiya tha.''"
2039,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Qais bin Makhrima sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko ye farmatey suna : kya main tum ko apney aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key barey main eik waqia bayan na karun? hamney kaha : haan zarur. unhoney farmaya : eik martaba meri raat ki baari thi jis mein aap merey yahaan they. aap (Isha ki namaz padh kar) lotey to apney jootey apney paaun key paas utaar kar rakh liye aur apni chadar ka kinara apney bistar par bichha liya. thodi der key baad jab aap ney ye khayal kiya ke main so gaee hun (aap uthey) aahisatagi sey jootey pehney, chupkey sey chadar pakdi, phir hauley sey darwaza khola aur baghair aawaz kiye nikal gaey. mainey fauran qamis pahni, odhni odhi, tehband baandha aur aap key peechhey chal padi yahan tak ke aap Baqee (qabristaan) main pahunch gaey aur teen dafa haath utha utha kar lambi duayen kin, phir aap wapis mudey to main bhi mudi. aap tez huye to main bhi tez ho gaee. aap bhagney lagey to main bhi bhagney lagi. aap ney daud laga di to mainey bhi daud laga di lekin main aap sey (aagey thi, lihaza) pehley pahunch gaee aur ghar mein dakhil ho gaee. abhi main leti hi thi ke aap tashrif ley aaye aur aap ney puchha : Aaisha ! tujhey kya huwa? tera saans chadha huwa hai. pet phulaa huwa hai? mainey kaha : ji ! kuch bhi nahin. aap ney farmaya : mujhey sach sach bata dey warna mujhey bareek-dekhne wale aur khabrdar-zaat bata deygi. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey maa baap aap par qurban ! phir mainey puri baat bata di. aap ney farmaya : tera hi wo wajood tha jo mainey aagey aagey dekha tha? mainey kaha : ji haan. aap ney merey seeney mein is zor sey mukka maara ke mujhey sakht takleef hui, phir farmaya : kya to samajhti thi ke Allah Taala aur us ka Rasool tujh par zulm kerengey? mainey (dil mein) kaha : logon sey jitna bhi chhupaya jaey, Allah Taala to usey janta hi hai. aap ney farmaya : jab tu ney mujhey uthtey dekha tha to Jibril merey paas aaye they lekin wo andar dakhil nahin huye kyonkey to kapdey utaar chuki thi. unhoney mujhey (halkey sey) bulaya ke tujhey pata nahin chalney diya. mainey bhi (hauley sey) jawab diya ke tujhey pata nahin chal saka. mera khayal tha ke to so chuki hai, is liye mainey tujhey jagaana munasib na samjha. mujhey khatra tha ke to darney lageygi. to Jibril alehissalam ney mujh sey kaha ke main Baqee jaaun aur unkey liye bakhshish ki dua karun. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (mujhey qabristaan janey ka moqey miley to) main kaisey dua karun? aap ney farmaya : to keh : (السلام Ali (Raziallahu anhu) اھل الدیار … … … وانا ان شاء اللہ بکم لاحقون),''us qabristaan key momineen aur musalmanon par salamti ho. aur Allah Taala hum mein sey pehley aaney walon aur peechhey rehney walon sab par reham farmaai aur agar Allah Taala ney chaha to hum bhi tumhein milney waley hain.''"
2040,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : eik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uthey, apney kapdey pehney aur phir nikal gaey. mainey apni laundi Barira (Raziallahu anha) sey kaha ke wo aap ka peechha kerey. us ney aap ka peechha kiya yahan tak ke aap Baqee (jannatul Baqi) main pahunch gaey aur uskey ibtidaai hissey mein khadey (dua kartey) rahey. jab tak Allah Taala ney chaha, phir wapis chal padey. Barira aap sey pehley pahunch gaee aur mujhey sab kuchh bata diya. (aap tashrif laye to) mainey aap sey kuchh na kaha yahan tak ke jab subah hui to phir mainey is baat ka tazkira aap sey kiya. aap ney farmaya : mujhey ( Allah Taala ki taraf sey huk dekar) kaha gaya tha ke main Baqee mein madfun (dafan hue) logon key liye dua'aey rehmat aur maghfirat karun."
2041,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke jab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki janib sey meri baari wali raat hoti to aap raat key aakhiri hissey mein Baqee (qabristaan) tashrif ley jatey aur yun farmatey : (السلام علیکم دار قوم مومنین … … … اللھم ! لاھل بقیع الغرقد),''aey momineeney qabristaan ! tum par salamti ho. hum aur tum kal ko waqt muqarrara par Allah Taala key samney pesh honey waley hain aur shafa'at waghera main eik dusrey ka sahara banney waley hain aur yaqinan jab Allah Taala ney chaha to hum bhi tum sey milney waley hain. aey Allah ! Baqee gharqad mein dafn huey musalmanon ko maaf farma."
2042,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab qabristaan jatey to farmatey : (السلام علیکم اھل الدیار من المومنین … … … أسال اللہ العافیۃ لنا ولکم),''aey is qabristaan key musalman aur momin basiyo ! tum par salamti ho. yaqinan hum bhi, Allah ney chaha to, tum sey milney waley hain. tum hum sey pehley aagey ho. hum tumharey peechhey aa rahey hain. mein apney liye aur tumharey liye Allah Taala sey khairiyat o salamti ki dua karta hun."
2043,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke jab Hazrat Najaashi (Rahmatullahi Alaih) faut huye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : unkey liye bakhshish ki dua karo.
2044,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jis din Habsha key badshah Najaashi (Rahmatullahi Alaih) faut huye, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usi din un ki wafat ki ittilaa hamein di aur farmaya : apney (Islaami) bhai key liye istighfar karo."
2045,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney qabristaan janey wali aurton aur qabron par ibadat-gaahen bananey walon aur chiragh jalaaney walon par lanat ki hai.
2046,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey kisi shakhs ka angaarey par bethna jis sey uskey kapdey jal jaeyn, qabr par bethney sey behtar hai."
2047,"Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabron par mat betho."
2048,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala un logon (yahud aur nasara) par lanat farmaai jinhonney apney Anbiya ki qabron ko ibadat-gaah banaya."
2049,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala un yahudiyon aur esaiyon par lanat farmaai jinhonney apney Anbiya ki qabron ko ibadat-gaah banaya."
2050,"Hazrat Bashir bin Khasaasiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath chal raha tha, aap chand musalmanon ki qabron key paas sey guzrey to farmaya : ye log (wafat ki wajeh sey) bahut ziyada shar sey bach gaey hain. phir aap kuchh mushrekin ki qabron key paas sey guzrey to farmaya : ye log (apni maut ki wajeh sey) bahut ziyada khair sey mehroom rahey. achcha aap ney tawajjoh farmaee to eik shakhs ko qabristaan mein jooton samet chaltey dekha to farmaya : oh, saaf rangey huye (rang kar saaf kiye huye) chamdey key jootey pehanney waley ! inhein utaar dey."
2051,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maiyat ko jab qabr mein rakh diya jata hai aur uskey sathi usey dafn karney key baad wapis aa jatey hain to wo unkey jooton ki aawaz sun raha hota hai."
2052,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Allah Taala key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maiyat ko jab qabr mein rakh diya jata hai aur uskey sathi usey dafn kar key wapis aa jatey hain to abhi wo unkey jooton ki aawaz sun raha hota hai ke uskey paas do farishtey aa jatey hain. wo usey bitha letey hain aur kehtey hain : to us aadmi key barey mein kya kehta tha? momin shakhs to kehta hai : main gawahi deta hun ke wo Allah key bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. usey kaha jata hai : to apney jahannami thikaney ko dekh. Allah Taala ney tujhey iskey bajaey jannati thikana dey diya hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo dono thikanon ko dekhta hai."
2053,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab maiyat ko qabr mein dafn kar diya jata hai aur uskey sathi us sey lot kar jatey hain to abhi wo unkey jooton ki aawaz sun raha hota hai ke uskey paas do farishtey aa jatey hain. wo usey bitha letey hain aur us sey kehtey hain : to us shakhs (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key barey mein kya kaha karta tha? momin kehta hai : main gawahi deta hun ke wo Allah Taala key bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. to usey kaha jata hai : to apney jahannami thikaney ko dekh. Allah Taala ney tujhey uskey bajaey achchha thikana dey diya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo dono thikanon ko dekhta hai. lekin kafir ya munafiq sey kaha jata hai : to us shakhs key barey mein kya kehta tha? to wo kehta hai : main kuchh nahin janta. jis tarah log kehtey they, main bhi kehta tha. usey (farishton ki taraf sey) kaha jata hai : na tu ney jan'ney ki koshish ki aur na tu ney Quran padha, phir uskey kanon key darmiyan (yani uskey chehrey par) sakht zarab lagai jati hai to wo is qadr cheekhta hai ke insan aur jinkey ilawa har qaribi makhluq uski aah aur bakaa (cheekh aur pukaar) sunti hai."
2054,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Yasar bayan kartey hain ke main Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Sard aur Khalid bin Arfata Raziallahu anhuma key paas betha tha ke logon ney eik shakhs ka zikr kiya jo pet ki takleef sey faut ho gaya tha. un dono mein sey har eik buzurg ney khahish zahir ki ke uskey janaazey mein shareek hon. un mein sey eik ney dusrey sey kaha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye nahin farmaya tha : jo aadmi pet ki takleef sey mar jaey, usey azabe-qabr nahin hoga? to dusrey ney kaha : kyon nahin ! (aap ney zarur farmaya tha)."
2055,Hazrat Raashid bin Saad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi sey bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya wajeh hai ke ehale eman ka un ki qabron mein imtihan liya jata hai magar shaheed ka nahin? aap ney farmaya : uskey sar par chamakti talwaaren uskey liye imtihan sey kafi ho gaeen.
2056,"Hazrat Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : taaoon, pet ki takleef, gharq aur dar-daza sey aaney wali maut shahadat hai. (Hadees key raawi Suleman (Alaihissalam) Taimi ney) kaha : hum sey ye hadees Abu-Usman ney kaee baar bayan ki. aur eik baar is ko (marfooa) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farman bayan kiya."
2057,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (Hazrat Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) key dafn key waqt ) farmaya : ye shakhs jis key liye arsh jhum gaya, is (ki rooh) key liye aasman key tamam darwazey khol diye gaey aur uskey janaazey par sattar hazar farishtey hazir huye, wo bhi bheench diya gaya magar phir usey chhod diya gaya."
2058,"Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ye aayat azabe-qabr key barey mein utri hai : (یثبت اللہ الذین امنوا … … … وفی الاخرۃ),''Allah taala momineen ko duniya aur aakhirat (qabr) main sahih baat par qaaim rakhta hai.''"
2059,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye aayat azabe-qabr key barey mein nazil hui hai : (یثبت اللہ الذین امنوا … … … وفی الاخرۃ),''Allah taala eman walon ko duniya aur aakhirat (qabr) main durust baat par qaaim rakhta hai. maiyat sey puchha jata hai : tera Rab kon hai? momin kehta hai : mera Rab Allah hai. aur merey Nabi Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hain.'' ye matlab hai is farmane-Ilaahi ka : (یثبت اللہ الذین امنوا … … … وفی الاخرۃ),''Allah taala eman walon ko duniya aur aakhirat (qabr) main sahih baat par qaaim rakhta hai.''"
2060,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik qabr sey aawaz suni to farmaya : ye kab faut huwa? logon ney bataya ke ye daure-jahiliyat mein faut huwa tha. to aap ko khushi hui, phir farmaya : agar ye khatra na ho ke tum mardon ko dafn nahin karogey to main Allah Taala sey dua karta ke wo tumhein azabe-qabr suna dey."
2061,Hazrat Abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghurub shams (suraj dubney) key baad bahar tashrif ley gaey. aap ney eik aawaz suni to farmaya : yahudiyon ko un ki qabron mein azab ho raha hai.
2062,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) yun dua farmaya kartey they : (اللھم انی أعوذبک من عذاب القبر … … … و أعوذبک من فتنۃ المسیح الدجال),''aey Allah ! main qabr key azab sey bachney key liye teri panah chahta hun. aur aag key azab sey bachney key liye teri panah chahta hun. aur zindagi aur maut key fitney sey teri panah chahta hun aur (jhootey) Masih Dajjaal key fitney sey teri panah mein aata hun.''"
2063,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko uskey baad azabe-qabr sey Allah Taala ki panah maangtey suna.
2064,"Hazrat Asma binte Abi Bakar (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (khutbey key liye) khadey huye to aap ney us aazmaaish ka zikr farmaya jis mein har shakhs ko qabr key andar mubtala hona padeyga. jab aap ney ye zikr farmaya to musalman aah aur bakaa (cheekh aur pukaar) karney lagey yahan tak ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka kalam na samajh saki. jab un ki aah aur bakaa (cheekh aur pukaar) ki aawaz ruk gaee to mainey eik qaribi shakhs sey kaha : Allah Taala terey liye barkat farmaai ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aakhir mein kya farmaya hai? us ney kaha : aap ney farmaya tha : mujhey ""wahi"" ki gaee hai ke qabron mein tumhari fitnaey-Dajjaal jaisi aazmaaish hogi."
2065,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ye dua sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ko Quran ki sura ki tarah sikhatey they, farmaya : tum kaho : (اللھم ! انا نعوذبک من عذاب جھنم … … … و أعوذبک من فتنۃ المحیا و الممات),''aey Allah ! hum jahannam key azab sey bachney key liye teri panah chahtey hain aur qabr key azab sey bachney key liye teri panah chahtey hain aur (jhootey) Masih Dajjaal ki aazmaaish sey bachney key liye teri panah chahtey hain aur zindagi aur maut key fitney sey bachney key liye teri panah chahtey hain.''"
2066,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : (eik dafa) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye to merey paas eik Yahudi aurat bethi thi aur wo keh rahi thi ke qabron main tumhara imtihan liya jaeyga (ya tumhein azab hoga). Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghabra gaey aur farmaya : sirf Yahud ko azab hoga. kuchh din guzrey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey ""wahi'' ki gaee hai ke qabron main tumhara imtihan hoga. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : uskey baad mainey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) azabe-qabr sey Allah Taala ki panah talab kiya kartey they."
2067,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) azabe-qabr aur fitnae-Dajjaal sey Allah Taala ki panah talab kiya kartey they aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabron main tumhara imtihan hoga.
2068,Hazrat Masruq sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi aurat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas aai aur un sey koi chiz maangi. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney wo chiz usey dey di. to usney kaha : Allah Taala tujhey azabe-qabr sey bachaey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mujhey is barey mein kuchh hichkichahat hui yahan tak ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to mainey ye baat aap sey bayan ki. aap ney farmaya : yaqinan un (yahudiyon) ko un ki qabron mein azab hota hai yahan tak ke janwer usey suntey hain.
2069,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : Madiney ki do Yahudi aurten merey paas aayin aur kehney lagin ke qabron walon ko un ki qabron mein azab hota hai. mainey in ko jhutlaaya. mera dil un ki tasdeeq par mutmain na huwa. wo chali gaeen to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! do boodhi Yahudi aurton ney kaha hai ke faut hone walon ko qabron mein azab hota hai. aap ney farmaya : wo sach kehti hain. in ko azab hota hai yahan tak ke janwer usey suntey hain. iskey baad mainey dekha ke jab bhi aap ney namaz padhi, azabe-qabr sey zarur panah talab ki."
2070,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama ya Madina Munawra key baghaat mein sey eik baagh sey guzrey to aap ney do insanon ki aawaz suni jinhein qabron mein azab ho raha tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : inhein azab ho raha hai aur kisi badi chiz key barey mein azab nahin ho raha. phir farmaya : kyon nahin ! (woh badi hi hai). un mein sey eik apney peshab sey bachta na tha aur doosra chughliyan khaya karta tha. phir aap ney eik chhadi mangwai, uskey do hissey kiye aur har qabr par eik eik tukda rakh diya. aap sey arz kiya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney aisey kyon kiya? aap ney farmaya : ummid hai unkey khushk honey tak inkey azab mein kami raheygi."
2071,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) do qabron key paas sey guzrey aur farmaya : in dono ko azab ho raha hai aur ye azab kisi badey kaam key barey mein nahin ho raha. in mein sey eik shakhs to apney peshab sey bachta na tha aur doosra chughliyan khaya karta tha. phir aap ney khajoor ki eik taza shaakh li, usey cheer kar do hissey kiye aur phir har qabr par eik hissa gaad diya. logon ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney aisey kyon kiya? aap ney farmaya : mujhey ummid hai jab tak ye khushk nahin hongi, in sey azab mein kami raheygi."
2072,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khabrdar ! jab tum mein sey koi shakhs faut ho jata hai to is par us ka thikana subah Sham pesh kiya jata hai. agar wo jannati ho to jannati thikana aur agar wo jahannami ho to jahannami thikana (aur ye silsila jari raheyga) yahan tak ke Allah Taala usey qiyamat key din qabr sey utha ley (to phir wo is mein dakhil ho jaeyga)."
2073,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi mar jata hai to is par us ka thikana subah Sham pesh kiya jata hai. agar wo jahannami ho to usey kaha jata hai ke ye hai tera asal thikana (lekin abhi to is mein nahin jaeyga) yahan tak ke Allah Taala tujhey qiyamat key din qabr sey uthaey."
2074,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs mar jata hai to is par us ka thikana subah Sham pesh kiya jata hai. agar wo jannati ho to jannati thikana pesh kiya jata hai aur agar wo jahannami ho to jahannami thikana pesh kiya jata hai aur usey kaha jata hai ke ye tera thikana hai yahan tak ke tujhey Allah Taala qiyamat key din is sey uthaey."
2075,Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin ki rooh (wafat key baad) jannat key darakhton mein udti rehti hai yahan tak ke Allah Taala qiyamat key din usey uskey jism mein dakhil karega.
2076,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hum Makka Mukarrama aur Madina Munawra key darmiyan Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key sath they. wo hamein Badr key kafir maqtooleen key barey mein bataaney lagey ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jang sey eik din qabl hamein unkey halak honey ki jaghen dikha rahey they. aap ney farmaya : Insha-Allah kal ye falan ki halakat-gaah hogi. Hazrat umr ney farmaya : qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko bar-haq Nabi banaya ! wo un jagahon sey zarra bhar bhi idhar-udhar nahin huye, phir unhein eik kunwen mein phenk diya gaya, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unkey paas (us kunwen par) gaey aur buland aawaz sey pukara : aey falan bin falan ! aey falan bin falan ! kya tum ney sach paai wo chiz jis ka tum sey tumharey Rab ney wada kiya tha? mainey to Allah key wadey ko sach paya hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aap aisey jismon sey baaten kar rahey hain jin mein rooh nahin? aap ney farmaya : tum meri baaton ko un sey ziyada sunney waley nahin."
2077,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke musalmanon ney (jange-badar key baad) raat ko Badr key kunwen par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khadey farmatey huye suna : aey Abu-Jahal bin Hisham ! aey Sheeba bin Rabeea ! aey Utba bin Rabeea ! aey Umayya bin Half ! kya tum ney apney Rab ka wada sach paya? mainey to apney Rab ka wada sach paya hai. logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap un logon ko pukar rahey hain jo laash ban chukey hain? aap ney farmaya : tum meri baat ko un sey ziyada nahin suntey magar wo jawab nahin dey saktey.
2078,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (jange-badar sey agley din) Badr key kunwen key kinarey ja khadey huye aur farmaya : kya tum ney apney Rab key wadey ko bar-haq paya? aap ney farmaya : ab ye meri baat ko ba-khoobi sun rahey hain. ye baat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey zikr ki gaee to unhoney farmaya : ibne-Umar ko ghalat fehmi ho gaee hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : ab wo ba-khoobi jaan chukey hain ke main jo kuchh in ko kehta raha hun, wo bilkul sach hai. phir unhoney Allah Taala ka ye farman padha (انک لا تسمع الموتی . ۔ . ۔),''yaqinan to mardon ko nahin suna sakta. unhoney puri aayat padhi.''"
2079,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (marney key baad) insan key tamam aa'zaa (angon) ko mitti kha leti hai siwaye reedh ki haddi ka aakhiri sirey ke. usi sey insan ki paidaish ki ibtida (shuruat) hui aur usi sey (dobara) jism joda jaeyga."
2080,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney farmaya : Adam ka beta meri takzeeb karta (jhutlaata) hai, halanke usey meri takzeeb jachti nahin. (isi tarah) Adam ka beta mujhey gaali deta hai, halanke usey jachta nahin ke wo mujhey gaali dey. us ka meri takzeeb karna (jhutlaana) to ye hai ke wo kehta hai : Allah Taala mujhey dobara paida nahin kar sakeyga, halanke mainey usey pehli dafa paida kiya hai aur dusri dafa banana merey liye pehli dafa sey mushkil nahin. aur us ka mujhey gaali dena ye hai ke wo kehta hai : Allah Taala ki bhi aulad hai, halanke main yaktaa Allah hun jis ko kisi ki koi zarurat nahin. na mujh sey koi paida huwa, na main kisi sey paida huwa aur na koi mera sathi hai."
2081,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : eik aadmi ney apney aap par bahut zulm kiya tha (bahut gunah kiye they) yahan tak ke uski wafat ka waqt aa gaya. us ney apney ghar walon sey kaha : jab main mar jaaun to mujhey jala dena, phir meri haddiyon ko pees lena, phir hawa waley din meri raakh samandar mein uda dena. Allah ki qism ! agar Allah Taala ney mujhey pakad liya to mujhey aisa azab deyga jo us ney apni makhluq mein sey kisi ko na diya hoga. uskey ghar walon ney aisey hi kiya. Allah Taala ney har us chiz ko, jis mein uskey jism ka koi hissa tha, hukm diya ke jo kuchh tujh mein us ka hissa hai, nikal dey. to nagahan wo Allah Taala key samney purey ka pura khada tha. Allah Taala ney farmaya : jo kuchh tu ney kiya, kis bina par kiya? us ney kaha : terey dar ki bina par. to Allah Taala ney usey maaf kar diya."
2082,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum sey pehley logon main eik aadmi apney aamal key barey mein bura guman rakhta tha (ke wo qabile-maafi nahin), lihaza jab uski wafat ka waqt qarib aaya to usney apney ghar walon sey kaha : jab main mar jaaun to mujhey jala dena, phir pees kar aataa kar dena, phir meri raakh ko samandar mein uda dena. agar Allah Taala ney mujh par qabu pa liya to mujhey hergiz maaf na kerega. Allah Taala ney farishton ko hukm diya to unhoney uski rooh nikal li, phir Allah Taala ney (us ka dhaanchaa hazir kiya aur) farmaya : jo kuchh tu ney kiya, kyon kiya? us ney kaha : aey merey Rab ! mainey jo kuchh kiya, terey dar sey kiya. to Allah Taala ney usey maaf kar diya."
2083,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko member par khutbey ki haalat mein ye farmatey huye suna : tum nangey paaun, nangey jism aur baghair khatnon key Allah Taala sey milogey."
2084,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din log nangey jism aur baghair khatnon key ikhattey kiye jaeyngey. aur insanon mein sey sab sey pehley Hazrat Ibrahim alehissalam ko kapdey pahnaaey jaeyngey, phir aap ney ye aayat tilawat farmaee : (کما بدانا اول خلق نعیدہ),''jaisey hamney isey pehli dafa paida kiya tha, wesay hi phir isey paltaaeyn-gey."
2085,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din sab log nangey paaun, nangey jism aur baghair khatnon key (qabron sey) uthaey jaeyngey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kiya : sharam-gaahon ka kya baneyga? aap ney farmaya : (لکل امریء منھم یومئذ شان یغنیہ),''har shakhs ki us din aisi haalat hogi jo usey (har chiz sey) be niyaz kar deygi.''"
2086,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba tumhein nangey paaun aur nangey jism (Allah taala key samney) jama kiya jaeyga. mainey kaha : mard aur aurten eik dusrey ko dekhengey? Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Aaisha ! soorate-haal itni holnaak hogi ke kisi ko is ka khayal bhi na aayega."
2087,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din log teen haalaton mein ikhattey kiye jaeyngey. eik giroh rehmat ki ummid rakhey huye apney anjam sey darta hoga. (aur doosra giroh) do aadmi eik oont par hongey ya teen aadmi eik oont par ya chaar eik oont par ya das aadmi eik oont par aur baqi logon (teesrey giroh) ko aag ikhatta karegi. jahan wo log dophare ko aaram key liye thehrengey, aag bhi wahan unkey sath thehreygi. aur jahan wo raat guzaarengey, aag bhi unkey sath raat guzaareygi. jahan wo subah kerengey, wahan aag bhi unkey sath subh keregi aur jahan wo Sham kerengey, wahin aag bhi unkey sath Sham keregi."
2088,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey bayan farmaya : log teen girohon ki surat mein ikhattey kiye jaeyngey : kuchh to sawar ho kar khatey peetey pehantey (khush khush) aayengey. aur kuchh logon ko farishtey chehron key bal ghaseet'tey huye laeyngey aur aag in ko ikhatta keregi. aur kuchh log pedal chaltey aur daudtey bhagtey, girtey padtey aayengey. Allah Taala sawari key janweron par koi wabaa dal deyga to wo khatam ho jaaeyngey (bahut hi kam reh jaaeyngey) yahan tak ke baagh wala aadmi apna pura baagh eik oontni key badley deney par tayyar hoga magar oontni na ley sakeyga."
2089,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) wa'z aur nasihat key liye khadey huye to farmaya : aey logo ! yaqinan tumhein Allah Taala key samney nangey jism, nangey paaun baghair khatney key jama kiya jaeyga. irshade Bari Taala hai : (کما بدانا اول خلق نعیدہ),''jis tarah hamney pehley paida kya tha, isi tarah hum paltaaeyngey.'' phir aap ney farmaya : qiyamat key din sab sey pehley Hazrat Ibrahim alehissalam ko libas pehnaya jaeyga. meri ummat key kuchh log laye jaeyngey, phir unhen baain taraf nikal liya jaeyga. main kahunga : aey merey Rab ! ye to meri ummat sey hain (ya merey sathi hain?) to kaha jaeyga : aap nahin jantey, unhoney aap ki adam (ghair) mojudgi mein kya kuchh kiya. to main (isi tarah) kahun ga : jis tarah Allah key nek bandey (Hazrat Esa Masih Alaihissalam) ka qol hai : (وکنت علیھم شھیدا ما دمت فیھم … … … وان تغفرلھم فانک انت العزیز الحکیم),''(aey Allah ! ) main to in par gawah tha jab tak mein in mein raha, jab tu ney mujhey apney qabzey mein ley liya, phir to tu hi in par nigraan tha (lihaza tujhey hi inkey kamon ka ilm hai) aur to har chiz par khub gawah hai, agar to azab dey to wo terey bandey hain aur agar bakhsh dey to be-shak to ghalib hai khub hikmat wala hai.'' phir kaha jaeyga : jab sey aap in ko chhod kar (hamarey paas) aagey ye usi waqt sey murtad ho gaey they aur murtad hi rahey."
2090,"Hazrat Qurra Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bethtey to aap key sath aap key sahaba mein sey kuchh na kuchh log betha kartey they. un main eik shakhs tha jis ka eik ma'soom beta tha. wo peechhey sey aata to baap usey apney aagey bitha leta tha. ittifaaq se wo bachcha faut ho gaya to wo shakhs apney betey ki yad mein (kaee roz tak) aap ki majlis mein hazir na huwa kyonkey usey us (ki wafat) ka shadeed gham tha. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey (kaee din) na dekha to farmaya : kya wajeh hai ke falan shakhs nazar nahin aata? logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! us ka wo chhota sa bachcha jo aap ney bhi dekha tha, faut ho gaya hai, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us shakhs sey miley aur uskey betey key barey mein puchha. us ney bataya ke wo to faut ho chuka hai. aap ney usey tasalli di. aap ney farmaya : aey shakhs ! tujhey kon si chiz ziyada pasand hai ke to apni sari umr us sey faeyda uthata (aankhen thandi karta) ya ye ke to jannat key jis darwazey key paas bhi jaey, usey wahan paey ke wo tujh sey pehley pahunch kar usey terey liye khol dey? us ney kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! mujhey ye baat ziyada pasand hai ke wo mujh sey pehley ja kar merey liye jannat ka darwaza kholey. aap ney farmaya : bas ! ye chiz tujhey mil jaaeygi."
2091,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke maut key farishtey ko Hazrat Musa alehissalam ki taraf ( insani surat mein) bheja gaya. jab wo farishta aaya to Musa alehissalam ney usey thappad maar kar uski aankh phod di. wo apney rab taala key paas wapis gaya aur arz kya : aey Allah ! tu ney mujhey aisey bandey ki taraf bheja jo marna nahin chahta. Allah Taala ney uski aankh durust farma di aur farmaya : uskey paas dobara ja aur usey keh ke apna haath kisi bail ki pusht par rakhey. usey har baal key iwaz, jo uskey haath key nichey aayega, eik saal zindagi milegi. (us sari karrawai key bad) Musa alehissalam ney kaha : aey merey rab ! phir kya hoga ? farmaya : ( phir ) maut ! unhoney kaha : phir abhi theek hai lekin unhoney Allah Taala sey ye guzarish ki ke mujhey eik pathar phainkney key fasley tak muqaddas sar zamin key qarib kar diya jaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar main wahan hota to tumhein raastey ki eik janib surkh rang key tiley key nichey un ki qabr dikhata."
